WEBVTT

﻿1
00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:12.074
Watch Online Movies and Series for FREE
www.osdb.link/lm

2
00:00:17.852 --> 00:00:19.854
(THEME MUSIC PLAYING)

3
00:02:45.083 --> 00:02:46.668
(BB-8 CHIRPING)

4
00:02:56.511 --> 00:02:58.846
This will begin to make things right.

5
00:02:59.764 --> 00:03:02.750
I've traveled too far and seen too much

6
00:03:02.850 --> 00:03:05.812
to ignore the despair in the galaxy.

7
00:03:05.937 --> 00:03:09.774
Without the Jedi. there can be
no balance in the Force.

8
00:03:10.608 --> 00:03:13.152
Well. because of you.
now we have a chance.

9
00:03:13.278 --> 00:03:15.029
The General's been after this
for a long time.

10
00:03:15.488 --> 00:03:16.890
Oh. the General?

11
00:03:16.990 --> 00:03:19.367
To me. she is royalty.

12
00:03:19.784 --> 00:03:21.352
Well. she certainly is that.

13
00:03:21.452 --> 00:03:23.788
- (SLATS CLATTERING)
- (BB-8 CHIRPING EXCITEDLY)

14
00:03:27.208 --> 00:03:28.376
We got company.

15
00:03:28.835 --> 00:03:30.587
(VILLAGERS SHOUTING INDISTINCTLY)

16
00:03:33.214 --> 00:03:34.424
(SHOUTING CONTINUES)

17
00:03:41.431 --> 00:03:42.974
You have to hide.

18
00:03:43.099 --> 00:03:44.517
You have to leave.

19
00:03:46.644 --> 00:03:47.645
Go.

20
00:03:47.812 --> 00:03:49.480
- (VILLAGERS CLAMORING)
- (BELL TOLLING)

21
00:03:52.984 --> 00:03:55.194
- (VILLAGER SCREAMS)
- (CLAMORING CONTINUES)

22
00:03:58.197 --> 00:03:59.532
(BLASTER COCKING)

23
00:04:05.955 --> 00:04:07.707
(INDISTINCT SCREAMING AND SHOUTING)

24
00:04:07.832 --> 00:04:09.834
(INDISTINCT STORMTROOPER RADIO CHATTER)

25
00:04:17.550 --> 00:04:18.885
(POE PANTING)

26
00:04:19.010 --> 00:04:21.346
- Come on. BB-8. hurry!
- (BB-8 CHIRPS)

27
00:04:27.185 --> 00:04:28.853
- (ENGINES REVVING)
- (BB-8 CHIRPS NERVOUSLY)

28
00:04:32.357 --> 00:04:33.483
(BB-8 CHIRPS)

29
00:04:33.608 --> 00:04:34.717
STORMTROOPER: Blast that X-wing!

30
00:04:34.817 --> 00:04:35.985
Over there! Over there!

31
00:04:36.444 --> 00:04:37.987
- (POE GROANS)
- (ALARMS RINGING)

32
00:04:41.032 --> 00:04:43.117
- (BB-8 CHIRPING)
- I see them.

33
00:04:57.048 --> 00:04:58.716
(VILLAGER CHITTERING NERVOUSLY)

34
00:05:14.732 --> 00:05:15.675
You take this.

35
00:05:15.775 --> 00:05:17.735
It's safer with you than it is with me.

36
00:05:18.569 --> 00:05:20.697
You get as far away from here as you can.

37
00:05:21.864 --> 00:05:23.574
- Do you hear me?
- (BB-8 CHIRPS)

38
00:05:23.700 --> 00:05:25.076
I'll come back for you.

39
00:05:25.743 --> 00:05:27.120
It will be all right.

40
00:05:30.248 --> 00:05:31.249
(BLASTER COCKING)

41
00:05:36.713 --> 00:05:37.964
(STORMTROOPER GROANS)

42
00:05:57.859 --> 00:05:59.235
(FN-2187 GASPING)

43
00:06:26.179 --> 00:06:27.472
STORMTROOPER 1: Keep moving!

44
00:06:29.640 --> 00:06:30.975
STORMTROOPER 2: Stay here.

45
00:06:54.373 --> 00:06:57.251
KYLO REN: Look how old you've become.

46
00:06:57.919 --> 00:07:00.880
Something far worse has happened to you.

47
00:07:01.672 --> 00:07:03.674
You know what I've come for.

48
00:07:04.050 --> 00:07:05.952
I know where you come from.

49
00:07:06.052 --> 00:07:08.012
Before you called yourself Kylo Ren.

50
00:07:08.513 --> 00:07:12.099
The map to Skywalker.
We know you found it.

51
00:07:13.267 --> 00:07:16.020
And now you're going
to give it to the First Order.

52
00:07:16.145 --> 00:07:18.589
The First Order rose from the dark side.

53
00:07:18.689 --> 00:07:19.690
You did not.

54
00:07:20.858 --> 00:07:23.361
I'll show you the dark side.

55
00:07:24.028 --> 00:07:25.680
You may try.

56
00:07:25.780 --> 00:07:29.784
But you cannot deny
the truth that is your family.

57
00:07:30.535 --> 00:07:31.561
You're so right.

58
00:07:31.661 --> 00:07:32.954
(LIGHTSABER CRACKLING)

59
00:07:39.335 --> 00:07:40.878
(BLASTER BOLT CRACKLING)

60
00:07:42.380 --> 00:07:43.506
(POE GROANS)

61
00:07:47.260 --> 00:07:48.886
(BOLT PULSATING)

62
00:07:53.474 --> 00:07:54.725
(GROANS)

63
00:08:05.611 --> 00:08:07.905
So. who talks first?
You talk first? I talk first?

64
00:08:09.073 --> 00:08:10.950
KYLO REN: The old man gave it to you.

65
00:08:11.117 --> 00:08:12.685
It's just very hard
to understand you with all the...

66
00:08:12.785 --> 00:08:14.412
- Search him.
- ...apparatus.

67
00:08:18.457 --> 00:08:20.334
- STORMTROOPER: Nothing. sir.
- KYLO REN: Put him on board.

68
00:08:26.465 --> 00:08:28.968
PHASMA: Sir. the villagers?

69
00:08:31.554 --> 00:08:32.763
- Kill them all.
- (BLASTERS COCKING)

70
00:08:32.972 --> 00:08:34.098
(VILLAGERS EXCLAIMING)

71
00:08:34.265 --> 00:08:35.850
PHASMA: On my command.

72
00:08:36.809 --> 00:08:38.169
Fire.

73
00:08:38.269 --> 00:08:40.271
- (VILLAGERS SCREAMING)
- POE: Please. no!

74
00:08:49.655 --> 00:08:51.490
(INDISTINCT STORMTROOPER RADIO CHATTER)

75
00:09:01.626 --> 00:09:02.960
(BOLT CRACKLING)

76
00:09:05.212 --> 00:09:06.589
(FN-2187 GASPS)

77
00:09:08.758 --> 00:09:10.551
STORMTROOPER: Nothing here. Go ahead!

78
00:09:14.138 --> 00:09:15.514
(BB-8 CHIRPS)

79
00:09:20.561 --> 00:09:22.146
(BB-8 MOANS SOFTLY)

80
00:09:30.613 --> 00:09:32.156
(CREATURE EXCLAIMS IN ALIEN DIALECT)

81
00:09:51.592 --> 00:09:52.660
All right.

82
00:09:52.760 --> 00:09:53.761
All right!

83
00:09:55.096 --> 00:09:57.014
(INDISTINCT PA CHATTER)

84
00:10:03.646 --> 00:10:05.189
(FN-2187 PANTING)

85
00:10:12.989 --> 00:10:14.490
(GASPING)

86
00:10:19.662 --> 00:10:21.372
PHASMA: FN-2187.

87
00:10:22.039 --> 00:10:24.542
Submit your blaster for inspection.

88
00:10:25.209 --> 00:10:26.460
Yes. Captain.

89
00:10:27.003 --> 00:10:29.714
And who gave you permission
to remove that helmet?

90
00:10:30.381 --> 00:10:31.365
I'm sorry. Captain.

91
00:10:31.465 --> 00:10:33.551
Report to my division at once.

92
00:11:22.600 --> 00:11:24.435
(PANTING)

93
00:12:15.820 --> 00:12:17.071
(SPEEDER REVVING)

94
00:12:47.143 --> 00:12:48.727
(REY SIGHS)

95
00:13:12.334 --> 00:13:13.444
- (STAFF CLACKS)
- (SCAVENGER 1 EXCLAIMS)

96
00:13:13.544 --> 00:13:14.904
(CHITTERING IN ALIEN DIALECT)

97
00:13:15.004 --> 00:13:16.755
(SCAVENGER 2 LAUGHING)

98
00:13:19.258 --> 00:13:22.511
UNKAR:
What you brought me today is worth...

99
00:13:22.636 --> 00:13:24.305
hmm...

100
00:13:25.556 --> 00:13:28.350
one quarter portion.

101
00:13:40.988 --> 00:13:43.073
(SPEEDER RACING)

102
00:14:11.268 --> 00:14:12.519
(SIZZLING)

103
00:14:23.364 --> 00:14:24.448
(FAINT BOOMING)

104
00:14:48.973 --> 00:14:51.433
(BB-8 CHIRPING FAINTLY)

105
00:14:54.353 --> 00:14:56.005
(BB-8 CHIRPING NERVOUSLY)

106
00:14:56.105 --> 00:14:58.315
(TEEDO SPEAKING ALIEN DIALECT)

107
00:15:01.694 --> 00:15:03.612
- (TEEDO EXCLAIMING)
- (BB-8 CHIRPING)

108
00:15:04.530 --> 00:15:06.240
(TEEDO SHOUTING IN ALIEN DIALECT)

109
00:15:06.824 --> 00:15:07.992
(SPEAKING ALIEN DIALECT)

110
00:15:08.117 --> 00:15:09.493
(TEEDO AND BB-8 EXCLAIMING)

111
00:15:09.660 --> 00:15:10.995
(SPEAKING ALIEN DIALECT)

112
00:15:12.496 --> 00:15:14.164
(REY SHOUTING IN ALIEN DIALECT)

113
00:15:16.292 --> 00:15:17.668
- (TEEDO CHITTERING)
- (BB-8 CHIRPING)

114
00:15:17.835 --> 00:15:20.629
(TEEDO AND REY ARGUING
IN ALIEN DIALECT)

115
00:15:23.340 --> 00:15:25.509
(TEEDO SCOFFS)

116
00:15:25.634 --> 00:15:28.012
- (BB-8 CHIRPS ANGRILY)
- Shh.

117
00:15:30.055 --> 00:15:32.349
That's just Teedo. Wants you for parts.

118
00:15:33.058 --> 00:15:34.643
He has no respect for anyone.

119
00:15:35.019 --> 00:15:36.020
(BB-8 EXCLAIMS SOFTLY)

120
00:15:38.355 --> 00:15:39.440
Your antenna's bent.

121
00:15:49.199 --> 00:15:50.242
Where do you come from?

122
00:15:50.409 --> 00:15:51.702
(BB-8 CHIRPING EXCITEDLY)

123
00:15:54.038 --> 00:15:55.814
- Classified. really?
- (CHIRPS MERRILY)

124
00:15:55.914 --> 00:15:57.207
Me too. Big secret.

125
00:15:58.125 --> 00:16:01.211
Niima Outpost is that way.
Stay off Kelvin Ridge.

126
00:16:01.378 --> 00:16:03.172
Keep away from
the Sinking Fields in the north.

127
00:16:03.339 --> 00:16:04.757
You'll drown in the sand.

128
00:16:05.632 --> 00:16:08.469
(BB-8 CHIRPING HAPPILY)

129
00:16:10.095 --> 00:16:12.973
Don't follow me. Town is that way.

130
00:16:13.098 --> 00:16:14.141
(BB-8 SIGHS)

131
00:16:14.850 --> 00:16:16.085
(BB-8 CHIRPS INQUISITIVELY)

132
00:16:16.185 --> 00:16:17.186
No!

133
00:16:18.270 --> 00:16:20.105
(BB-8 MOANS DEJECTEDLY)

134
00:16:28.989 --> 00:16:31.367
(BB-8 CHIRPING MERRILY)

135
00:16:33.577 --> 00:16:35.204
In the morning. you go.

136
00:16:36.955 --> 00:16:38.665
(BB-8 CHIRPS HAPPILY)

137
00:16:41.001 --> 00:16:42.127
You're welcome.

138
00:16:53.847 --> 00:16:57.935
KYLO REN: I had no idea we had
the best pilot in the Resistance on board.

139
00:17:00.354 --> 00:17:01.355
Comfortable?

140
00:17:01.939 --> 00:17:02.940
Not really.

141
00:17:04.400 --> 00:17:05.692
I'm impressed.

142
00:17:08.195 --> 00:17:13.492
No one has been able to get out of you
what you did with the map.

143
00:17:13.992 --> 00:17:16.328
You might want to rethink your technique.

144
00:17:18.414 --> 00:17:20.207
(DULL HUMMING)

145
00:17:21.834 --> 00:17:23.043
(POE GRUNTS SOFTLY)

146
00:17:24.670 --> 00:17:26.380
(POE GROANING)

147
00:17:31.802 --> 00:17:34.138
- (POE GRUNTS)
- Where is it?

148
00:17:36.098 --> 00:17:39.810
(STRAINING) The Resistance...
will not be intimidated by you.

149
00:17:43.981 --> 00:17:46.775
Where... is it?

150
00:17:47.401 --> 00:17:48.402
(GRUNTS)

151
00:17:52.322 --> 00:17:54.032
(YELLING)

152
00:17:56.743 --> 00:17:59.480
It's in a droid. A BB unit.

153
00:17:59.580 --> 00:18:02.024
Well. then. if it's on Jakku.
we'll soon have it.

154
00:18:02.124 --> 00:18:03.792
I leave that to you.

155
00:18:05.752 --> 00:18:08.614
REY: Don't give up hope.
He still might show up.

156
00:18:08.714 --> 00:18:10.824
Whoever it is you're waiting for.

157
00:18:10.924 --> 00:18:12.384
Classified.

158
00:18:13.093 --> 00:18:15.137
I know all about waiting.

159
00:18:15.345 --> 00:18:16.513
(BB-8 CHIRPS INQUISITIVELY)

160
00:18:16.763 --> 00:18:18.182
For my family.

161
00:18:18.849 --> 00:18:21.602
They'll be back. One day.

162
00:18:22.394 --> 00:18:23.395
Come on.

163
00:18:26.398 --> 00:18:29.568
UNKAR: These five pieces are worth...

164
00:18:30.402 --> 00:18:32.529
Let me see here... hmm...

165
00:18:32.905 --> 00:18:35.599
one half portion.

166
00:18:35.699 --> 00:18:37.409
Last week they were a half portion each.

167
00:18:37.534 --> 00:18:39.203
What about the droid?

168
00:18:42.039 --> 00:18:43.081
What about him?

169
00:18:43.207 --> 00:18:45.375
I'll pay for him.

170
00:18:47.711 --> 00:18:50.047
- (METAL CLANKS)
- (NIIMA TRADERS MURMURING)

171
00:18:51.256 --> 00:18:53.550
Sixty portions.

172
00:18:53.717 --> 00:18:55.552
(TRADERS EXCLAIMING)

173
00:19:05.562 --> 00:19:06.563
Actually...

174
00:19:08.565 --> 00:19:10.484
The droid's not for sale.

175
00:19:12.819 --> 00:19:13.820
Come on.

176
00:19:16.323 --> 00:19:18.016
- (METAL CLATTERS)
- (UNKAR GRUNTS)

177
00:19:18.116 --> 00:19:20.494
Follow the girl and get that droid.

178
00:19:24.331 --> 00:19:25.791
FN-2187: Ren wants the prisoner.

179
00:19:35.175 --> 00:19:36.301
FN-2187: Turn here.

180
00:19:38.262 --> 00:19:39.246
Listen carefully.

181
00:19:39.346 --> 00:19:41.582
If you do exactly as I say.
I can get you out of here.

182
00:19:41.682 --> 00:19:42.683
What?

183
00:19:43.934 --> 00:19:46.003
This is a rescue. I'm helping you escape.

184
00:19:46.103 --> 00:19:47.838
Can you fly a TIE fighter?

185
00:19:47.938 --> 00:19:48.981
You're with the Resistance?

186
00:19:49.106 --> 00:19:51.008
What? No. no. no. I'm breaking you out.

187
00:19:51.108 --> 00:19:53.110
- Can you fly a TIE fighter?
- I can fly anything.

188
00:19:53.860 --> 00:19:56.446
Why? Why are you helping me?

189
00:19:57.823 --> 00:19:59.533
Because it's the right thing to do.

190
00:20:00.450 --> 00:20:01.493
You need a pilot.

191
00:20:01.618 --> 00:20:02.953
I need a pilot.

192
00:20:04.454 --> 00:20:05.539
We're gonna do this.

193
00:20:05.872 --> 00:20:06.873
Yeah?

194
00:20:07.708 --> 00:20:09.001
(INDISTINCT PA CHATTER)

195
00:20:11.169 --> 00:20:13.363
FN-2187: Okay. Stay calm. Stay calm.

196
00:20:13.463 --> 00:20:15.966
- I am calm.
- I'm talking to myself.

197
00:20:18.468 --> 00:20:19.469
FN-2187: Not yet.

198
00:20:21.346 --> 00:20:23.056
Okay. go. This way.

199
00:20:29.313 --> 00:20:31.381
I've always wanted to fly
one of these things.

200
00:20:31.481 --> 00:20:33.550
- Can you shoot?
- Blasters. I can.

201
00:20:33.650 --> 00:20:34.968
Okay. same principle.

202
00:20:35.068 --> 00:20:37.821
Use the toggle on the left to switch
between missiles. cannons and mag pulse.

203
00:20:37.946 --> 00:20:39.364
Use the sight on the right to aim.

204
00:20:39.781 --> 00:20:41.575
- Triggers to fire.
- This is very complicated.

205
00:20:42.993 --> 00:20:44.661
(ION ENGINES FIRING)

206
00:20:46.538 --> 00:20:47.998
(CABLE CLANKS)

207
00:20:48.165 --> 00:20:49.249
POE: I can fix this.

208
00:20:52.586 --> 00:20:55.072
We have an unsanctioned
departure from bay two.

209
00:20:55.172 --> 00:20:57.924
Alert General Hux. And stop that fighter.

210
00:21:18.612 --> 00:21:22.866
- OFFICER: Fourteen failed. Eighteen...
- POE: I got it.

211
00:21:24.576 --> 00:21:26.203
(ENGINES ROARING)

212
00:21:26.787 --> 00:21:28.330
(EXCLAIMS) This thing really moves.

213
00:21:32.918 --> 00:21:35.087
We gotta take out as many of
these cannons as we can...

214
00:21:35.253 --> 00:21:36.280
or we're not gonna get very far.

215
00:21:36.380 --> 00:21:37.781
- All right.
- I'm gonna get us in position.

216
00:21:37.881 --> 00:21:38.882
Just stay sharp.

217
00:21:42.094 --> 00:21:43.662
Up ahead! Up ahead! You see it?

218
00:21:43.762 --> 00:21:44.788
I got us dead center.

219
00:21:44.888 --> 00:21:46.014
- It's a clean shot.
- Okay. got it.

220
00:21:54.773 --> 00:21:56.174
- Yeah!
- Yes!

221
00:21:56.274 --> 00:21:57.342
(YELLING) Did you see that?

222
00:21:57.442 --> 00:21:59.069
- Did you see that?
- I saw it!

223
00:22:04.741 --> 00:22:05.851
Hey. what's your name?

224
00:22:05.951 --> 00:22:07.185
FN-2187.

225
00:22:07.285 --> 00:22:08.478
POE: F... What?

226
00:22:08.578 --> 00:22:10.414
That's the only name they ever gave me.

227
00:22:10.539 --> 00:22:12.983
Well. I ain't using it. F-N. huh?

228
00:22:13.083 --> 00:22:14.568
Finn. I'm gonna call you Finn.

229
00:22:14.668 --> 00:22:16.278
- Is that all right?
- Finn.

230
00:22:16.378 --> 00:22:18.030
Yeah. Finn. I like that.

231
00:22:18.130 --> 00:22:20.282
- I like that.
- I'm Poe. Poe Dameron.

232
00:22:20.382 --> 00:22:22.300
- Good to meet you. Poe.
- Good to meet you too. Finn.

233
00:22:24.428 --> 00:22:25.787
(ALARM BEEPING)

234
00:22:25.887 --> 00:22:28.306
OFFICER:
Sir. they've taken out our turbolasers.

235
00:22:29.099 --> 00:22:30.475
Use the ventral cannons.

236
00:22:30.809 --> 00:22:32.711
Yes. sir. Bringing them online.

237
00:22:32.811 --> 00:22:35.505
KYLO REN:
General Hux. is it the Resistance pilot?

238
00:22:35.605 --> 00:22:39.484
Yes. and he had help from one of our own.

239
00:22:40.277 --> 00:22:43.488
We're checking the registers now
to identify which stormtrooper it was.

240
00:22:43.613 --> 00:22:46.992
The one from the village. FN-2187.

241
00:22:47.617 --> 00:22:49.411
Sir. ventral cannons hot.

242
00:22:49.953 --> 00:22:50.954
Fire.

243
00:23:00.338 --> 00:23:01.990
One's coming toward you!
My right. Your left.

244
00:23:02.090 --> 00:23:03.842
- Do you see it?
- Hold on.

245
00:23:03.967 --> 00:23:04.968
- I see him!
- (FIRING LASERS)

246
00:23:08.346 --> 00:23:09.848
Nice shot!

247
00:23:16.188 --> 00:23:17.272
Where are we going?

248
00:23:17.397 --> 00:23:18.523
We're going back to Jakku. That's where.

249
00:23:18.648 --> 00:23:20.175
No. We can't go back to Jakku.

250
00:23:20.275 --> 00:23:21.718
We need to get out of this system.

251
00:23:21.818 --> 00:23:23.695
I gotta get my droid
before the First Order does.

252
00:23:23.820 --> 00:23:25.055
- What. a droid?
- That's right.

253
00:23:25.155 --> 00:23:27.365
He's a BB unit. orange and white.
One of a kind.

254
00:23:27.491 --> 00:23:28.475
I don't care what color he is!

255
00:23:28.575 --> 00:23:29.810
No droid can be that important.

256
00:23:29.910 --> 00:23:30.894
This one is. pal!

257
00:23:30.994 --> 00:23:32.662
We gotta get as far away from
the First Order as we can.

258
00:23:32.788 --> 00:23:34.064
We go back to Jakku. we die.

259
00:23:34.164 --> 00:23:36.858
That droid has a map
that leads straight to Luke Skywalker.

260
00:23:36.958 --> 00:23:38.877
Oh. you gotta be kidding me! (GRUNTS)

261
00:23:41.963 --> 00:23:45.050
PHASMA: FN-2187 reported to my division...

262
00:23:45.175 --> 00:23:47.452
was evaluated. and sent to reconditioning.

263
00:23:47.552 --> 00:23:49.788
No prior signs of nonconformity?

264
00:23:49.888 --> 00:23:51.790
This was his first offense.

265
00:23:51.890 --> 00:23:52.999
OFFICER: General!

266
00:23:53.099 --> 00:23:54.459
- They've been hit.
- Destroyed?

267
00:23:54.559 --> 00:23:55.794
Disabled.

268
00:23:55.894 --> 00:23:57.295
They were headed back to Jakku.

269
00:23:57.395 --> 00:23:59.589
The fighter is projected to crash
in the Goazon badlands.

270
00:23:59.689 --> 00:24:01.358
They were going back for the droid.

271
00:24:01.483 --> 00:24:03.401
Send a squad to the wreckage.

272
00:24:03.819 --> 00:24:05.195
(GASPS)

273
00:24:08.698 --> 00:24:09.699
(GROANS)

274
00:24:25.757 --> 00:24:26.925
FINN: (FAINTLY) Poe!

275
00:24:28.260 --> 00:24:29.553
Poe!

276
00:24:30.387 --> 00:24:31.429
Poe!

277
00:24:34.891 --> 00:24:36.393
Poe! I got you.

278
00:24:38.562 --> 00:24:39.563
Poe!

279
00:24:41.106 --> 00:24:42.691
(SHIP CREAKING)

280
00:24:46.403 --> 00:24:47.445
Poe!

281
00:25:55.513 --> 00:25:56.806
(PANTING)

282
00:26:11.655 --> 00:26:13.865
HUX: Supreme Leader Snoke was explicit.

283
00:26:14.032 --> 00:26:16.434
Capture the droid if we can.
but destroy it if we must.

284
00:26:16.534 --> 00:26:18.328
KYLO REN:
How capable are your soldiers. General?

285
00:26:18.453 --> 00:26:19.896
I won't have you question my methods.

286
00:26:19.996 --> 00:26:22.040
They're obviously skilled
at committing high treason.

287
00:26:22.165 --> 00:26:24.960
Perhaps Leader Snoke should
consider using a clone army.

288
00:26:25.085 --> 00:26:26.111
My men are exceptionally trained.

289
00:26:26.211 --> 00:26:27.404
Programmed from birth.

290
00:26:27.504 --> 00:26:29.781
Then they should have
no problem retrieving the droid.

291
00:26:29.881 --> 00:26:30.882
Unharmed.

292
00:26:31.967 --> 00:26:34.119
Careful. Ren. that your
personal interests...

293
00:26:34.219 --> 00:26:36.680
not interfere with orders
from Leader Snoke.

294
00:26:36.846 --> 00:26:39.249
I want that map.

295
00:26:39.349 --> 00:26:40.725
For your sake...

296
00:26:40.850 --> 00:26:42.060
I suggest you get it.

297
00:26:48.650 --> 00:26:49.801
(PANTING) Water. Water.

298
00:26:49.901 --> 00:26:50.927
MERCHANT: (IN THICK ACCENT) No water.

299
00:26:51.027 --> 00:26:52.529
- FINN: Water.
- (TRADER GRUNTS LOUDLY)

300
00:26:54.406 --> 00:26:55.473
(PANTS) Is there water?

301
00:26:55.573 --> 00:26:57.200
(MERCHANT EXCLAIMING IN ALIEN DIALECT)

302
00:27:02.330 --> 00:27:03.873
(WATER SPLASHING)

303
00:27:15.051 --> 00:27:16.052
(SPUTTERING)

304
00:27:21.391 --> 00:27:23.768
(THUG SPEAKING ALIEN DIALECT)

305
00:27:23.935 --> 00:27:26.254
- What? Oi. get off him!
- (BB-8 CHIRPS)

306
00:27:26.354 --> 00:27:27.731
- (REY YELPS)
- (THUG GROANS)

307
00:27:31.276 --> 00:27:32.485
- (BB-8 EXCLAIMS)
- (REY GRUNTS)

308
00:27:35.739 --> 00:27:36.740
Hey!

309
00:27:40.744 --> 00:27:41.745
(BB-8 CHIRPS)

310
00:27:45.415 --> 00:27:46.750
(BB-8 CHIRPS INQUISITIVELY)

311
00:27:51.755 --> 00:27:53.006
(BB-8 CHIRPING)

312
00:27:53.131 --> 00:27:55.175
REY: They work for Unkar.

313
00:27:55.300 --> 00:27:57.035
That guy that wanted you.

314
00:27:57.135 --> 00:27:58.762
He must have really wanted you.

315
00:27:59.637 --> 00:28:00.930
(BB-8 EXCLAIMS LOUDLY)

316
00:28:01.139 --> 00:28:03.016
- (BB-8 CHIRPING)
- REY: Who?

317
00:28:03.933 --> 00:28:06.102
- (BB-8 CHIRPS EXCITEDLY)
- Him?

318
00:28:21.534 --> 00:28:22.660
(GRUNTS)

319
00:28:22.869 --> 00:28:24.037
(GROANS)

320
00:28:24.913 --> 00:28:28.083
- What's your hurry. thief?
- What? Thief?

321
00:28:28.249 --> 00:28:29.693
- (ZAPPING)
- Ow!

322
00:28:29.793 --> 00:28:31.069
- Hey. what?
- The jacket.

323
00:28:31.169 --> 00:28:32.670
This droid says you stole it.

324
00:28:33.630 --> 00:28:35.298
I've had a pretty messed up
day. all right?

325
00:28:35.423 --> 00:28:37.842
So I'd appreciate it
if you stop accusing me of...

326
00:28:37.967 --> 00:28:40.370
- Ow! Stop it!
- Where'd you get it?

327
00:28:40.470 --> 00:28:41.805
It belongs to his master.

328
00:28:45.100 --> 00:28:48.186
It belonged to Poe Dameron.
That was his name. right?

329
00:28:50.230 --> 00:28:52.857
He was captured by the First Order.

330
00:28:52.982 --> 00:28:55.568
I helped him escape. but our ship crashed.

331
00:28:58.696 --> 00:28:59.823
Poe didn't make it.

332
00:29:00.990 --> 00:29:02.367
(BB-8 MOANS DEJECTEDLY)

333
00:29:04.661 --> 00:29:06.830
I tried to help him. I'm sorry.

334
00:29:15.004 --> 00:29:16.714
So you're with the Resistance?

335
00:29:21.344 --> 00:29:22.679
Obviously.

336
00:29:22.846 --> 00:29:24.122
Yes. I am.

337
00:29:24.222 --> 00:29:25.515
I'm with the Resistance. yeah.

338
00:29:25.640 --> 00:29:27.684
(WHISPERS) I am with the Resistance.

339
00:29:28.893 --> 00:29:31.312
I've never met
a Resistance fighter before.

340
00:29:32.856 --> 00:29:34.299
Well. this is what we look like.

341
00:29:34.399 --> 00:29:36.926
Some of us. Others look different.

342
00:29:37.026 --> 00:29:38.470
BB-8 says he's on a secret mission.

343
00:29:38.570 --> 00:29:40.071
He has to get back to your base.

344
00:29:40.196 --> 00:29:44.200
Apparently. he has a map that leads to
Luke Skywalker and everyone's after it.

345
00:29:44.826 --> 00:29:46.536
(WHISPERS) Luke Skywalker?

346
00:29:47.078 --> 00:29:48.580
I thought he was a myth.

347
00:29:48.788 --> 00:29:50.874
- (BB-8 CHIRPING RAPIDLY)
- What?

348
00:29:54.836 --> 00:29:56.796
(THUG SPEAKING ALIEN DIALECT)

349
00:29:58.882 --> 00:30:00.425
- What are you doing?
- Come on.

350
00:30:01.718 --> 00:30:02.886
FINN: Come on. BB-8!

351
00:30:06.222 --> 00:30:07.724
- REY: Let go of me!
- Come on. we gotta move!

352
00:30:07.849 --> 00:30:09.934
I know how to run
without you holding my hand!

353
00:30:12.520 --> 00:30:14.297
REY: BB-8. stay close!

354
00:30:14.397 --> 00:30:15.398
This way.

355
00:30:17.233 --> 00:30:18.985
(TRADERS SHOUTING IN ALIEN DIALECT)

356
00:30:21.196 --> 00:30:22.405
STORMTROOPER: Call in the air strike.

357
00:30:23.239 --> 00:30:24.782
FINN: Come on!

358
00:30:26.242 --> 00:30:27.452
REY: They're shooting at both of us.

359
00:30:27.577 --> 00:30:29.454
Yeah. They saw you with me. You're marked.

360
00:30:29.579 --> 00:30:30.980
- Well. thanks for that.
- Hey!

361
00:30:31.080 --> 00:30:32.916
I'm not the one who chased
you down with a stick.

362
00:30:33.041 --> 00:30:34.083
(BB-8 CHIRPING)

363
00:30:34.209 --> 00:30:35.693
(SHOUTING)
Does anyone have blasters around here?

364
00:30:35.793 --> 00:30:37.320
- Are you okay?
- (BB-8 CHIRPING)

365
00:30:37.420 --> 00:30:38.696
(FINN SHUSHING)

366
00:30:38.796 --> 00:30:41.049
(DISTANT ION ENGINES ROARING)

367
00:30:42.884 --> 00:30:44.302
Stop taking my hand!

368
00:30:47.764 --> 00:30:48.890
(BOTH GRUNTING)

369
00:30:51.851 --> 00:30:53.378
(ALL CLAMORING)

370
00:30:53.478 --> 00:30:55.104
(ENGINES ROARING)

371
00:31:00.610 --> 00:31:01.611
Hey.

372
00:31:03.071 --> 00:31:04.072
(GRUNTS)

373
00:31:04.906 --> 00:31:05.949
Are you okay?

374
00:31:07.951 --> 00:31:08.952
Yeah.

375
00:31:09.619 --> 00:31:10.745
Follow me.

376
00:31:22.298 --> 00:31:24.909
- FINN: We can't outrun them!
- We might in that quadjumper!

377
00:31:25.009 --> 00:31:26.344
Hey. we need a pilot!

378
00:31:26.469 --> 00:31:28.012
We've got one.

379
00:31:28.137 --> 00:31:29.138
You?

380
00:31:29.806 --> 00:31:31.749
Uh. what about that ship?

381
00:31:31.849 --> 00:31:33.309
That one's garbage!

382
00:31:38.815 --> 00:31:40.275
The garbage will do.

383
00:31:50.159 --> 00:31:51.452
(BB-8 CHIRPS)

384
00:31:56.165 --> 00:31:57.875
Gunner position is down there!

385
00:32:01.129 --> 00:32:02.755
You ever fly this thing?

386
00:32:02.880 --> 00:32:06.009
No! This ship hasn't flown in years.

387
00:32:06.175 --> 00:32:07.176
Great.

388
00:32:11.389 --> 00:32:12.598
Whoa.

389
00:32:13.224 --> 00:32:14.809
I can do this. I can do this.

390
00:32:15.226 --> 00:32:16.853
I can do this. I can do this.

391
00:32:18.730 --> 00:32:20.023
(THRUSTERS FIRING)

392
00:32:29.991 --> 00:32:31.451
- (REY YELPS)
- (FINN GRUNTS)

393
00:32:38.041 --> 00:32:39.042
UNKAR: Hey!

394
00:32:43.379 --> 00:32:44.922
That's mine!

395
00:32:48.509 --> 00:32:50.094
Wait. stay low! Hey. stay low!

396
00:32:50.219 --> 00:32:51.287
- What?
- FINN: (ON RADIO) Stay low!

397
00:32:51.387 --> 00:32:52.597
It confuses their tracking.

398
00:32:52.972 --> 00:32:54.891
- BB-8. hold on!
- (BB-8 CHIRPS)

399
00:32:55.058 --> 00:32:56.434
I'm going low!

400
00:33:04.609 --> 00:33:06.569
- (REY GASPS)
- (BB-8 EXCLAIMS)

401
00:33:13.868 --> 00:33:14.911
(GRUNTS)

402
00:33:15.078 --> 00:33:16.287
What are you doing back there?

403
00:33:16.412 --> 00:33:17.580
Are you ever gonna fire back?

404
00:33:17.747 --> 00:33:19.791
I'm working on it! Are the shields up?

405
00:33:19.916 --> 00:33:21.584
Not so easy without a co-pilot!

406
00:33:21.751 --> 00:33:23.628
Try sitting in this thing.

407
00:33:26.381 --> 00:33:27.507
(REY GRUNTS)

408
00:33:31.469 --> 00:33:32.720
(LASERS FIRING)

409
00:33:37.934 --> 00:33:39.268
We need cover. quick!

410
00:33:39.435 --> 00:33:40.712
We're about to get some!

411
00:33:40.812 --> 00:33:42.021
(SOFTLY) I hope.

412
00:33:42.188 --> 00:33:43.398
(HULL CREAKING)

413
00:34:07.713 --> 00:34:09.215
Damn it!

414
00:34:13.261 --> 00:34:14.762
(ENGINE REVVING)

415
00:34:20.184 --> 00:34:21.978
Come on. come on!

416
00:34:24.814 --> 00:34:27.066
- Nice shot!
- I'm getting pretty good at this.

417
00:34:29.777 --> 00:34:31.404
(SCAVENGER EXCLAIMING IN ALIEN DIALECT)

418
00:34:39.287 --> 00:34:40.980
(CONTROLS CLICKING)

419
00:34:41.080 --> 00:34:42.690
Uh. the cannon's stuck
in forward position.

420
00:34:42.790 --> 00:34:44.459
I can't move it. You gotta lose him!

421
00:34:44.625 --> 00:34:45.793
(REY PANTING)

422
00:34:48.337 --> 00:34:50.840
- Get ready!
- Okay. For what?

423
00:35:04.645 --> 00:35:05.771
Are we really doing this?

424
00:35:12.278 --> 00:35:13.362
(REY GRUNTS)

425
00:35:15.198 --> 00:35:16.532
Oh. no.

426
00:35:37.970 --> 00:35:38.971
Whoo!

427
00:35:53.361 --> 00:35:54.846
- REY: Nice shooting.
- Now that was some flying.

428
00:35:54.946 --> 00:35:55.930
- Thanks.
- How did you do that?

429
00:35:56.030 --> 00:35:57.306
- I don't know.
- No one trained you?

430
00:35:57.406 --> 00:35:59.142
I've flown some ships. but
I've never left the planet.

431
00:35:59.242 --> 00:36:00.393
- Your last shot was dead-on.
- That was amazing.

432
00:36:00.493 --> 00:36:01.811
- You got him with one blast!
- You set me up for it.

433
00:36:01.911 --> 00:36:03.271
- It was perfect.
- That was pretty good.

434
00:36:03.371 --> 00:36:04.372
(CHIRPS INQUISITIVELY)

435
00:36:04.997 --> 00:36:06.791
(CHIRPS NERVOUSLY)

436
00:36:06.916 --> 00:36:08.918
You're okay. He's with the Resistance.

437
00:36:10.294 --> 00:36:11.921
He's gonna get you home.

438
00:36:13.047 --> 00:36:14.048
We both will.

439
00:36:19.887 --> 00:36:21.013
I don't know your name.

440
00:36:22.974 --> 00:36:24.517
Finn. What's yours?

441
00:36:25.810 --> 00:36:27.103
I'm Rey.

442
00:36:31.649 --> 00:36:32.984
- Rey...
- (PIPE BURSTING)

443
00:36:33.609 --> 00:36:35.887
REY: Help me with this. Quick!

444
00:36:35.987 --> 00:36:37.363
FINN: Whoa. what's going on?

445
00:36:37.488 --> 00:36:38.906
(REY GRUNTS)

446
00:36:48.624 --> 00:36:52.503
Sir... we were unable
to acquire the droid on Jakku.

447
00:36:54.964 --> 00:36:58.801
It escaped capture aboard a stolen
Corellian YT model freighter.

448
00:37:00.344 --> 00:37:02.413
The droid...

449
00:37:02.513 --> 00:37:04.140
stole a freighter?

450
00:37:04.265 --> 00:37:05.641
Not exactly. sir.

451
00:37:06.309 --> 00:37:07.310
It had help.

452
00:37:10.938 --> 00:37:14.525
We have no confirmation but we believe
FN-2187 may have helped in the escape.

453
00:37:14.984 --> 00:37:16.193
(LIGHTSABER ACTIVATING)

454
00:37:16.319 --> 00:37:17.862
(LIGHTSABER CRACKLING)

455
00:37:21.907 --> 00:37:23.743
(INSTRUMENTS SMASHING)

456
00:37:30.124 --> 00:37:31.500
(LIGHTSABER DEACTIVATING)

457
00:37:32.877 --> 00:37:33.878
Anything else?

458
00:37:36.756 --> 00:37:38.174
The two were accompanied by a girl.

459
00:37:40.426 --> 00:37:41.844
(CHOKING)

460
00:37:43.596 --> 00:37:45.348
What girl?

461
00:37:45.681 --> 00:37:47.308
(INSTRUMENTS BEEPING RAPIDLY)

462
00:37:48.059 --> 00:37:49.126
It's the motivator.

463
00:37:49.226 --> 00:37:50.711
Grab me a Harris wrench. check in there.

464
00:37:50.811 --> 00:37:51.796
How bad is it?

465
00:37:51.896 --> 00:37:53.564
If we wanna live. not good.

466
00:37:53.689 --> 00:37:54.632
They're hunting for us now.

467
00:37:54.732 --> 00:37:55.900
We've gotta get out of this system!

468
00:37:56.025 --> 00:37:58.736
BB-8 said the location of the
Resistance base is "need to know".

469
00:37:58.861 --> 00:38:00.471
If I'm taking you there. I need to know!

470
00:38:00.571 --> 00:38:01.572
This?

471
00:38:02.823 --> 00:38:04.450
(QUIETLY)
You gotta tell us where your base is.

472
00:38:04.575 --> 00:38:07.144
- (BB-8 CHIRPS)
- I don't speak that.

473
00:38:07.244 --> 00:38:08.980
(WHISPERS) All right. between us...

474
00:38:09.080 --> 00:38:10.539
I'm not with the Resistance. okay?

475
00:38:11.540 --> 00:38:13.109
I'm just trying to get away
from the First Order.

476
00:38:13.209 --> 00:38:14.944
But you tell us where the base is...

477
00:38:15.044 --> 00:38:16.462
I'll get you there first. Deal?

478
00:38:17.546 --> 00:38:20.049
- Droid. please!
- Pilex driver. hurry.

479
00:38:20.174 --> 00:38:22.802
- So. where's your base?
- Go on. BB-8. tell her.

480
00:38:26.013 --> 00:38:27.014
(WHISPERS) Please.

481
00:38:27.556 --> 00:38:28.933
(BB-8 CHIRPING)

482
00:38:29.058 --> 00:38:30.935
- The Ileenium system?
- Yeah. the Ileenium system.

483
00:38:31.060 --> 00:38:32.687
That's the one. Get us there
as fast as you can.

484
00:38:33.062 --> 00:38:34.397
I'll drop you two at Ponemah Terminal.

485
00:38:34.563 --> 00:38:35.631
I need the bonding tape. hurry!

486
00:38:35.731 --> 00:38:36.799
What about you?

487
00:38:36.899 --> 00:38:38.109
I gotta get back to Jakku.

488
00:38:38.234 --> 00:38:39.176
Back to Jak...

489
00:38:39.276 --> 00:38:40.720
Why does everyone wanna go back to Jakku?

490
00:38:40.820 --> 00:38:43.406
- It's not that one. No. No.
- That place is...

491
00:38:43.531 --> 00:38:45.391
The one I'm pointing to. No.

492
00:38:45.491 --> 00:38:46.784
(LOUDLY) No. No!

493
00:38:46.909 --> 00:38:48.244
If we don't patch it up...

494
00:38:48.411 --> 00:38:51.188
the propulsion tank will overflow
and flood the ship with poisonous gas!

495
00:38:51.288 --> 00:38:52.289
- This?
- Yes.

496
00:38:53.666 --> 00:38:56.485
Hey. Rey. you're a pilot.

497
00:38:56.585 --> 00:38:58.487
You can fly anywhere. Why go back?

498
00:38:58.587 --> 00:38:59.864
You got a family?

499
00:38:59.964 --> 00:39:01.090
You got a boyfriend? A cute boyfriend?

500
00:39:01.215 --> 00:39:02.658
None of your business. that's why.

501
00:39:02.758 --> 00:39:04.218
(POWER DRAINING)

502
00:39:05.094 --> 00:39:06.470
- That can't be good.
- No. it can't be.

503
00:39:10.349 --> 00:39:11.392
(FLICKING SWITCHES)

504
00:39:12.435 --> 00:39:13.436
Someone's locked on to us.

505
00:39:13.561 --> 00:39:15.104
All controls are overridden.

506
00:39:15.396 --> 00:39:16.480
(DULL CLANGING)

507
00:39:21.902 --> 00:39:23.612
Get off! Get off!

508
00:39:25.364 --> 00:39:26.365
See anything?

509
00:39:27.825 --> 00:39:28.826
FINN: Oh. no.

510
00:39:37.084 --> 00:39:38.069
It's the First Order.

511
00:39:38.169 --> 00:39:39.962
What do we do? There must be something.

512
00:39:40.755 --> 00:39:42.406
- You said poisonous gas.
- I fixed that.

513
00:39:42.506 --> 00:39:43.507
Can you unfix it?

514
00:39:49.305 --> 00:39:50.306
REY: Come on. BB-8.

515
00:39:51.056 --> 00:39:52.933
FINN: I got him. (YELPS)

516
00:39:54.268 --> 00:39:56.020
- (POWER RETURNING)
- FINN: I'm okay.

517
00:39:56.854 --> 00:39:58.397
- (REY STRAINING)
- FINN: BB-8. get off me!

518
00:39:58.522 --> 00:40:00.483
- (BB-8 CHIRPING)
- (DULL THUDDING)

519
00:40:01.275 --> 00:40:02.927
Do you think this will work
on the stormtroopers?

520
00:40:03.027 --> 00:40:05.571
Yeah. Their masks filter out
smoke. not toxins.

521
00:40:09.200 --> 00:40:11.243
- (METAL CLANGING)
- (FOOTSTEPS APPROACHING)

522
00:40:12.953 --> 00:40:14.121
- FINN: Hurry.
- I'm hurrying.

523
00:40:16.540 --> 00:40:17.708
(METAL WHIRRING)

524
00:40:26.217 --> 00:40:28.619
Chewie...

525
00:40:28.719 --> 00:40:29.970
we're home.

526
00:40:30.554 --> 00:40:32.097
(CHEWIE GROWLS)

527
00:40:35.643 --> 00:40:37.269
(CHEWIE GROWLS SOFTLY)

528
00:40:37.770 --> 00:40:38.854
- (FLICKS SWITCH)
- (CONTROLS BEEP)

529
00:40:39.021 --> 00:40:40.189
(OBJECT CLATTERS)

530
00:40:45.986 --> 00:40:47.138
Where are the others?

531
00:40:47.238 --> 00:40:48.806
- Where's the pilot?
- REY: I'm the pilot.

532
00:40:48.906 --> 00:40:50.349
- You?
- (CHEWIE GROWLS)

533
00:40:50.449 --> 00:40:52.393
No. it's true.
We're the only ones on board.

534
00:40:52.493 --> 00:40:53.911
FINN: You can understand that thing?

535
00:40:54.036 --> 00:40:56.272
And "that thing" can
understand you. too. so watch it.

536
00:40:56.372 --> 00:40:58.290
- Come on out of there.
- (CHEWIE GROWLS)

537
00:40:58.999 --> 00:41:00.876
- Where'd you get this ship?
- Niima Outpost.

538
00:41:01.001 --> 00:41:03.529
Jakku? That junkyard?

539
00:41:03.629 --> 00:41:04.822
Thank you! Junkyard.

540
00:41:04.922 --> 00:41:06.991
Told you we should have
double-checked the Western Reaches.

541
00:41:07.091 --> 00:41:08.826
- (CHEWIE GROWLS)
- Who had it? Ducain?

542
00:41:08.926 --> 00:41:10.745
REY: I stole it. From Unkar Plutt.

543
00:41:10.845 --> 00:41:13.055
He stole it from the Irving Boys.
who stole it from Ducain.

544
00:41:13.180 --> 00:41:15.458
Who stole it from me!

545
00:41:15.558 --> 00:41:16.959
Well. you tell him that Han Solo...

546
00:41:17.059 --> 00:41:19.436
just stole back the
Millennium Falcon for good.

547
00:41:19.562 --> 00:41:22.439
This is the Millennium Falcon?
You're Han Solo?

548
00:41:24.066 --> 00:41:25.609
I used to be.

549
00:41:26.277 --> 00:41:27.720
Han Solo. the Rebellion general?

550
00:41:27.820 --> 00:41:29.180
No. the smuggler.

551
00:41:29.280 --> 00:41:31.098
- Wasn't he a war hero?
- (CHEWIE GRUNTS)

552
00:41:31.198 --> 00:41:34.518
This is the ship that made
the Kessel Run in 14 parsecs?

553
00:41:34.618 --> 00:41:35.870
Twelve!

554
00:41:36.954 --> 00:41:38.414
(SCOFFS) Fourteen.

555
00:41:53.762 --> 00:41:54.930
Hey!

556
00:41:55.431 --> 00:41:58.417
Some moof-milker
put a compressor on the ignition line.

557
00:41:58.517 --> 00:41:59.585
REY: Unkar Plutt did.

558
00:41:59.685 --> 00:42:01.045
I thought it was a mistake. too.
Puts too much...

559
00:42:01.145 --> 00:42:03.439
BOTH: ...stress on the hyperdrive.

560
00:42:04.481 --> 00:42:05.941
Chewie. throw them in a pod.

561
00:42:06.066 --> 00:42:07.927
We'll drop them at the
nearest inhabited planet.

562
00:42:08.027 --> 00:42:09.720
- (CHEWIE GROWLS)
- REY: Wait. no.

563
00:42:09.820 --> 00:42:12.223
- We need your help.
- My help?

564
00:42:12.323 --> 00:42:15.242
This droid has to get to the
Resistance base as soon as possible.

565
00:42:15.951 --> 00:42:18.329
He's carrying a map to Luke Skywalker.

566
00:42:22.833 --> 00:42:25.753
You are the Han Solo that
fought with the Rebellion.

567
00:42:31.842 --> 00:42:32.843
You knew him.

568
00:42:36.180 --> 00:42:39.291
Yeah. I knew him.

569
00:42:39.391 --> 00:42:41.018
I knew Luke.

570
00:42:41.602 --> 00:42:42.603
(DULL THUDDING)

571
00:42:43.812 --> 00:42:46.106
Don't tell me a Rathtar's gotten loose.

572
00:42:46.774 --> 00:42:47.775
FINN: Wait. what?

573
00:42:48.692 --> 00:42:50.361
Did you just say Rathtars?

574
00:42:51.111 --> 00:42:52.096
Hey!

575
00:42:52.196 --> 00:42:54.740
You're not hauling Rathtars
on this freighter. are you?

576
00:42:55.282 --> 00:42:57.476
- I'm hauling Rathtars.
- (CHEWIE GROWLS SOFTLY)

577
00:42:57.576 --> 00:43:00.771
Oh. great. It's the Guavian Death Gang.

578
00:43:00.871 --> 00:43:02.331
Must have tracked us from Nantoon.

579
00:43:02.456 --> 00:43:04.233
- (CHEWIE GROWLS)
- What's a Rathtar?

580
00:43:04.333 --> 00:43:05.818
They're big and they're dangerous.

581
00:43:05.918 --> 00:43:07.444
You ever heard of the Trillia Massacre?

582
00:43:07.544 --> 00:43:08.571
- No.
- FINN: Good.

583
00:43:08.671 --> 00:43:10.531
I got three of them going to King Prana.

584
00:43:10.631 --> 00:43:12.950
Three? How'd you get them on board?

585
00:43:13.050 --> 00:43:14.760
I used to have a bigger crew.

586
00:43:15.260 --> 00:43:16.303
(CHEWIE GROWLS)

587
00:43:16.428 --> 00:43:18.180
(BB-8 CHIRPING)

588
00:43:18.347 --> 00:43:20.249
HAN:
Get below and stay there until I say so...

589
00:43:20.349 --> 00:43:21.917
and don't even think about
taking the Falcon.

590
00:43:22.017 --> 00:43:23.002
What about BB-8?

591
00:43:23.102 --> 00:43:24.795
He stays with me
until I get rid of the gang...

592
00:43:24.895 --> 00:43:26.422
then you can have him back
and be on your way.

593
00:43:26.522 --> 00:43:28.465
What about the Rathtars?
Where are you keeping them?

594
00:43:28.565 --> 00:43:29.984
- (LOUD THUDDING)
- (BOTH YELP)

595
00:43:30.901 --> 00:43:32.928
- There's one.
- What are you gonna do?

596
00:43:33.028 --> 00:43:35.306
Same thing I always do.
Talk my way out of it.

597
00:43:35.406 --> 00:43:36.557
(CHEWIE GROWLS)

598
00:43:36.657 --> 00:43:38.909
Yes. I do. Every time.

599
00:43:56.176 --> 00:43:58.162
Han Solo.

600
00:43:58.262 --> 00:43:59.722
You're a dead man.

601
00:43:59.847 --> 00:44:02.558
Bala-Tik. What's the problem?

602
00:44:02.766 --> 00:44:05.436
The problem is we loaned you
50.000 for this job.

603
00:44:05.602 --> 00:44:08.063
- (WHISPERS) Can you see them?
- No.

604
00:44:08.230 --> 00:44:11.233
I heard you also borrowed
50.000 from Kanjiklub.

605
00:44:11.442 --> 00:44:13.569
You know you can't trust
those little freaks.

606
00:44:14.236 --> 00:44:16.639
How long we known each other?

607
00:44:16.739 --> 00:44:17.806
They have blasters.

608
00:44:17.906 --> 00:44:18.974
A lot of them.

609
00:44:19.074 --> 00:44:22.269
BALA-TIK:
Not long. We want our money back now.

610
00:44:22.369 --> 00:44:24.355
HAN: You think hunting Rathtars is cheap?

611
00:44:24.455 --> 00:44:25.606
I spent that money.

612
00:44:25.706 --> 00:44:28.125
Kanjiklub wants
their investment back. too.

613
00:44:28.250 --> 00:44:30.527
I never made a deal with Kanjiklub!

614
00:44:30.627 --> 00:44:32.488
BALA-TIK: Tell that to Kanjiklub.

615
00:44:32.588 --> 00:44:34.006
(AIRLOCK CLANKING)

616
00:44:41.805 --> 00:44:43.999
Tasu Leech.

617
00:44:44.099 --> 00:44:45.100
Good to see you.

618
00:44:45.559 --> 00:44:47.352
(SPEAKING ALIEN DIALECT)

619
00:44:49.354 --> 00:44:51.231
(CONTINUES SPEAKING ALIEN DIALECT)

620
00:44:53.942 --> 00:44:56.929
Boys. you're both gonna
get what I promised.

621
00:44:57.029 --> 00:44:58.389
Have I ever not delivered...

622
00:44:58.489 --> 00:44:59.990
- for you before?
- Yeah.

623
00:45:04.286 --> 00:45:07.289
- What was the second time?
- BALA-TIK: Your game is old.

624
00:45:07.414 --> 00:45:09.917
There's no one in the galaxy
left for you to swindle.

625
00:45:12.586 --> 00:45:13.570
That BB unit.

626
00:45:13.670 --> 00:45:16.507
The First Order is looking
for one just like it.

627
00:45:20.010 --> 00:45:21.303
And two fugitives.

628
00:45:25.182 --> 00:45:26.308
First I've heard of it.

629
00:45:32.147 --> 00:45:33.315
REY: Wait. wait. wait.

630
00:45:36.485 --> 00:45:39.763
If we close the blast doors in that
corridor we can trap both gangs!

631
00:45:39.863 --> 00:45:41.306
We'll close the blast doors from here?

632
00:45:41.406 --> 00:45:43.200
Resetting the fuses should do it.

633
00:45:46.370 --> 00:45:47.996
(RATHTARS GROWLING)

634
00:45:48.622 --> 00:45:50.082
(RATHTARS ROARING FAINTLY)

635
00:45:51.166 --> 00:45:52.943
I got a bad feeling about this.

636
00:45:53.043 --> 00:45:55.170
- Oh. no.
- "Oh. no." what?

637
00:45:56.130 --> 00:45:57.114
Wrong fuses.

638
00:45:57.214 --> 00:45:58.382
- Kill them!
- (BLASTERS COCKING)

639
00:45:58.507 --> 00:45:59.716
- Whoa...
- And take the droid!

640
00:46:00.342 --> 00:46:02.344
- (THUGS SCREAMING)
- (RATHTAR GROWLING)

641
00:46:05.180 --> 00:46:07.015
(THUGS CLAMORING)

642
00:46:09.893 --> 00:46:11.186
(CHEWIE YELPS)

643
00:46:13.063 --> 00:46:14.523
(RATHTAR SCREECHING)

644
00:46:17.568 --> 00:46:18.735
(THUG GROANS)

645
00:46:19.528 --> 00:46:20.946
(RATHTAR ROARS)

646
00:46:23.824 --> 00:46:24.825
(RATHTAR BELCHES)

647
00:46:25.534 --> 00:46:27.369
- This was a mistake!
- Huge!

648
00:46:27.536 --> 00:46:29.037
(THUG YELLING)

649
00:46:35.085 --> 00:46:37.045
(RATHTAR ROARS FAINTLY)

650
00:46:40.591 --> 00:46:41.592
REY: What do they look like?

651
00:46:43.886 --> 00:46:45.637
- (RATHTAR GROWLING)
- (THUG SCREAMING)

652
00:46:47.556 --> 00:46:49.558
They look like that.

653
00:46:51.810 --> 00:46:53.645
- FINN: This way.
- Are you sure?

654
00:46:55.564 --> 00:46:56.732
No. no. no!

655
00:46:57.774 --> 00:46:59.151
- Finn!
- (YELPS)

656
00:47:00.152 --> 00:47:01.236
Finn!

657
00:47:02.404 --> 00:47:03.405
Rey!

658
00:47:05.282 --> 00:47:06.475
(REY YELPS)

659
00:47:06.575 --> 00:47:07.868
FINN: Get off! Get off!

660
00:47:10.954 --> 00:47:12.247
(RATHTAR HOWLS FAINTLY)

661
00:47:13.290 --> 00:47:15.626
- (FAINTLY) Rey!
- Finn!

662
00:47:16.835 --> 00:47:17.920
Finn!

663
00:47:18.587 --> 00:47:20.255
FINN: (FAINTLY ON MONITOR) Get off me!

664
00:47:22.132 --> 00:47:23.467
(FINN GROANING FAINTLY)

665
00:47:27.095 --> 00:47:29.389
- (MONITOR BEEPING)
- (FINN SCREAMING FAINTLY)

666
00:47:31.934 --> 00:47:33.435
FINN: (FAINTLY) Rey!

667
00:47:34.394 --> 00:47:35.771
(FINN YELLING)

668
00:47:36.480 --> 00:47:39.358
- (RATHTAR ROARS FAINTLY)
- Get off! Get off!

669
00:47:40.609 --> 00:47:41.652
(GRUNTING)

670
00:47:41.777 --> 00:47:43.278
- Finn!
- (SHRIEKS)

671
00:47:43.946 --> 00:47:46.281
- It had me! But the door...
- That was lucky.

672
00:47:50.327 --> 00:47:52.621
- I got the door. Cover us!
- (CHEWIE ROARS)

673
00:47:56.500 --> 00:47:57.626
(BB-8 YELPS)

674
00:47:59.461 --> 00:48:01.338
- (CHEWIE ROARS)
- Chewie!

675
00:48:04.216 --> 00:48:05.801
- You okay?
- (CHEWIE GRUNTS)

676
00:48:06.969 --> 00:48:07.970
Wow.

677
00:48:10.180 --> 00:48:12.391
- Come on! Come on!
- (CHEWIE EXCLAIMS)

678
00:48:16.144 --> 00:48:17.129
Han.

679
00:48:17.229 --> 00:48:19.481
You. close the door behind us.
You. take care of Chewie!

680
00:48:19.856 --> 00:48:20.899
(CHEWIE ROARS)

681
00:48:21.566 --> 00:48:23.986
- (FLICKING SWITCHES)
- (SHIP POWERING UP)

682
00:48:27.155 --> 00:48:28.390
Hey. where are you going?

683
00:48:28.490 --> 00:48:30.142
Unkar Plutt installed a fuel pump. too.

684
00:48:30.242 --> 00:48:32.035
If we don't prime that.
we're not going anywhere.

685
00:48:32.160 --> 00:48:33.328
I hate that guy.

686
00:48:33.453 --> 00:48:35.939
- And you could use a co-pilot.
- I got one. he's back there.

687
00:48:36.039 --> 00:48:37.040
(CHEWIE GROANS)

688
00:48:38.417 --> 00:48:40.377
Watch the thrust. We're going
out of here at lightspeed.

689
00:48:40.502 --> 00:48:42.279
From inside the hangar?
Is that even possible?

690
00:48:42.379 --> 00:48:44.615
I never ask that question
till after I've done it.

691
00:48:44.715 --> 00:48:46.508
- (RATHTAR GROWLS)
- (REY YELPS)

692
00:48:46.883 --> 00:48:49.011
This is not how I thought
this day was gonna go.

693
00:48:49.136 --> 00:48:51.079
Angle the shield. Hang on back there.

694
00:48:51.179 --> 00:48:52.347
No problem!

695
00:49:02.274 --> 00:49:03.525
Come on. baby. don't let me down.

696
00:49:06.069 --> 00:49:08.030
- What?
- Compressor.

697
00:49:09.156 --> 00:49:10.782
(THRUSTERS FIRING)

698
00:49:12.868 --> 00:49:14.411
(LOUD BOOMING)

699
00:49:16.538 --> 00:49:19.650
Inform the First Order
that Han Solo has the droid they want.

700
00:49:19.750 --> 00:49:21.752
And it's aboard the Millennium Falcon.

701
00:49:23.128 --> 00:49:24.921
(ION ENGINES ROARING)

702
00:49:30.677 --> 00:49:35.057
SNOKE: The droid will soon be
delivered to the Resistance...

703
00:49:36.266 --> 00:49:40.062
leading them to the last Jedi.

704
00:49:41.271 --> 00:49:45.025
If Skywalker returns...

705
00:49:45.567 --> 00:49:49.571
the new Jedi will rise.

706
00:49:50.739 --> 00:49:52.282
Supreme Leader.
I take full responsibility...

707
00:49:52.407 --> 00:49:54.076
General!

708
00:49:56.286 --> 00:49:59.081
Our strategy must now change.

709
00:49:59.206 --> 00:50:01.249
The weapon. It is ready.

710
00:50:01.375 --> 00:50:03.627
I believe the time has come to use it.

711
00:50:03.752 --> 00:50:06.530
We shall destroy the government
that supports the Resistance...

712
00:50:06.630 --> 00:50:08.323
the Republic.

713
00:50:08.423 --> 00:50:11.635
Without their friends to protect them
the Resistance will be vulnerable.

714
00:50:11.885 --> 00:50:14.788
And we will stop them
before they reach Skywalker.

715
00:50:14.888 --> 00:50:16.139
Go.

716
00:50:16.932 --> 00:50:18.333
Oversee preparations.

717
00:50:18.433 --> 00:50:20.102
Yes. Supreme Leader.

718
00:50:26.066 --> 00:50:27.442
SNOKE: There has been an awakening.

719
00:50:29.152 --> 00:50:30.904
Have you felt it?

720
00:50:32.447 --> 00:50:33.490
KYLO REN: Yes.

721
00:50:34.866 --> 00:50:36.493
There's something more.

722
00:50:38.036 --> 00:50:42.207
The droid we seek is aboard
the Millennium Falcon.

723
00:50:42.999 --> 00:50:45.861
In the hands of your father...

724
00:50:45.961 --> 00:50:49.798
Han Solo.

725
00:50:52.426 --> 00:50:54.803
He means nothing to me.

726
00:50:54.928 --> 00:50:59.724
Even you. master of the Knights of Ren...

727
00:51:00.350 --> 00:51:03.812
have never faced such a test.

728
00:51:04.438 --> 00:51:07.649
By the grace of your training.
I will not be seduced.

729
00:51:08.775 --> 00:51:10.610
We shall see.

730
00:51:13.196 --> 00:51:15.031
We shall see.

731
00:51:21.872 --> 00:51:22.998
(FUSE BLOWING)

732
00:51:23.123 --> 00:51:25.333
- Electrical overload.
- I can fix that.

733
00:51:25.459 --> 00:51:26.710
Coolant's leaking.

734
00:51:26.835 --> 00:51:27.944
(ALARM BEEPING)

735
00:51:28.044 --> 00:51:30.781
- Try transferring auxiliary power...
- BOTH: ...to the secondary tank.

736
00:51:30.881 --> 00:51:32.424
- I got it.
- (CHEWIE GROWLING)

737
00:51:32.591 --> 00:51:34.217
FINN: Chewie. come on!

738
00:51:35.844 --> 00:51:37.412
I need help with this giant hairy thing!

739
00:51:37.512 --> 00:51:38.513
- Stop moving!
- (BB-8 CHIRPS)

740
00:51:38.638 --> 00:51:40.457
- (CHEWIE ROARS)
- (BB-8 YELPS)

741
00:51:40.557 --> 00:51:42.350
- FINN: Chewie!
- (BB-8 CHIRPING)

742
00:51:42.476 --> 00:51:44.186
You hurt Chewie.
you're gonna deal with me!

743
00:51:44.311 --> 00:51:46.646
Hurt him? He almost killed me six times!

744
00:51:47.564 --> 00:51:49.024
(CHOKING) Which is fine!

745
00:51:49.149 --> 00:51:52.652
This hyperdrive blows. there are gonna be
pieces of us in three different systems.

746
00:51:52.777 --> 00:51:54.613
(HYPERDRIVE NORMALIZING)

747
00:51:56.031 --> 00:51:57.032
What'd you do?

748
00:51:58.074 --> 00:51:59.993
I bypassed the compressor.

749
00:52:02.329 --> 00:52:03.330
Huh.

750
00:52:06.583 --> 00:52:07.876
Move. ball.

751
00:52:08.668 --> 00:52:09.878
(CHEWIE GROWLS)

752
00:52:10.045 --> 00:52:12.114
Ah. don't say that.

753
00:52:12.214 --> 00:52:13.882
You did great. Just rest.

754
00:52:14.799 --> 00:52:15.884
Good job. kid.

755
00:52:16.343 --> 00:52:17.344
Thanks.

756
00:52:17.886 --> 00:52:19.162
- You're welcome.
- (DEVICE HUMS)

757
00:52:19.262 --> 00:52:20.847
(HOLOGRAMS CHITTERING)

758
00:52:23.934 --> 00:52:26.811
HAN: So... fugitives. huh?

759
00:52:28.730 --> 00:52:30.006
REY: The First Order wants the map.

760
00:52:30.106 --> 00:52:31.399
Finn is with the Resistance.

761
00:52:32.025 --> 00:52:33.443
I'm just a scavenger.

762
00:52:35.487 --> 00:52:36.488
Let's see what you got.

763
00:52:37.364 --> 00:52:39.449
- (BB-8 CHIRPS INQUISITIVELY)
- Go ahead.

764
00:52:48.583 --> 00:52:50.735
- (CHEWIE EXCLAIMS)
- HAN: This map's not complete.

765
00:52:50.835 --> 00:52:52.337
It's just a piece.

766
00:52:53.547 --> 00:52:57.451
Ever since Luke disappeared
people have been looking for him.

767
00:52:57.551 --> 00:52:59.052
REY: Why did he leave?

768
00:53:00.262 --> 00:53:02.998
He was training a new generation of Jedi.

769
00:53:03.098 --> 00:53:07.143
One boy. an apprentice.
turned against him. destroyed it all.

770
00:53:08.728 --> 00:53:10.630
Luke felt responsible.

771
00:53:10.730 --> 00:53:13.233
He just walked away from everything.

772
00:53:13.942 --> 00:53:15.402
Do you know what happened to him?

773
00:53:15.569 --> 00:53:17.946
A lot of rumors. Stories.

774
00:53:19.948 --> 00:53:22.158
People that knew him best...

775
00:53:23.660 --> 00:53:26.037
think he went looking
for the first Jedi temple.

776
00:53:27.789 --> 00:53:29.107
The Jedi were real?

777
00:53:29.207 --> 00:53:31.401
I used to wonder about that myself.

778
00:53:31.501 --> 00:53:33.712
Thought it was a bunch of mumbo-jumbo.

779
00:53:34.588 --> 00:53:37.157
A magical power holding
together good and evil...

780
00:53:37.257 --> 00:53:39.384
the dark side and the light.

781
00:53:40.760 --> 00:53:42.929
Crazy thing is...

782
00:53:45.724 --> 00:53:46.766
it's true.

783
00:53:49.311 --> 00:53:50.937
The Force. The Jedi.

784
00:53:53.523 --> 00:53:54.524
All of it.

785
00:53:57.777 --> 00:53:59.095
It's all true.

786
00:53:59.195 --> 00:54:00.780
(TERMINAL BEEPING)

787
00:54:02.365 --> 00:54:04.492
- (CHEWIE GROWLS)
- No. you rest.

788
00:54:04.618 --> 00:54:07.354
- (CHEWIE GRUMBLES)
- You want my help? You're getting it.

789
00:54:07.454 --> 00:54:09.497
Gonna see an old friend.
She'll get your droid home.

790
00:54:10.790 --> 00:54:12.125
This is our stop.

791
00:54:29.517 --> 00:54:32.395
I didn't know there was this much green
in the whole galaxy.

792
00:54:57.253 --> 00:54:58.838
(BIRDS CHIRPING)

793
00:55:00.382 --> 00:55:02.425
Hey. Solo. I'm not sure what
we're walking into here...

794
00:55:02.550 --> 00:55:04.160
Did you just call me Solo?

795
00:55:04.260 --> 00:55:05.870
Sorry. Han. Mr. Solo.

796
00:55:05.970 --> 00:55:07.038
You should know...

797
00:55:07.138 --> 00:55:09.499
I'm a big deal in the Resistance.

798
00:55:09.599 --> 00:55:11.935
Which puts a real target on my back.

799
00:55:12.060 --> 00:55:13.628
Are there any conspirators here?

800
00:55:13.728 --> 00:55:15.605
Like. First Order sympathizers?

801
00:55:15.730 --> 00:55:18.383
Listen. Big Deal.

802
00:55:18.483 --> 00:55:20.385
You got another problem.

803
00:55:20.485 --> 00:55:22.654
Women always figure out the truth.

804
00:55:24.239 --> 00:55:25.573
Always.

805
00:55:31.579 --> 00:55:32.956
You might need this.

806
00:55:34.249 --> 00:55:35.917
I think I can handle myself.

807
00:55:36.042 --> 00:55:38.153
I know you do. That's why
I'm giving it to you.

808
00:55:38.253 --> 00:55:39.254
Take it.

809
00:55:42.090 --> 00:55:43.241
You know how to use one of those?

810
00:55:43.341 --> 00:55:44.993
Yeah. You pull the trigger.

811
00:55:45.093 --> 00:55:46.928
Little bit more to it than that.

812
00:55:47.429 --> 00:55:49.097
You got a lot to learn.

813
00:55:50.515 --> 00:55:51.766
You got a name?

814
00:55:52.684 --> 00:55:53.685
Rey.

815
00:55:54.394 --> 00:55:55.395
Rey.

816
00:55:59.274 --> 00:56:01.676
I been thinking about bringing
on some more crew. Rey.

817
00:56:01.776 --> 00:56:03.720
A second mate. Someone to help out.

818
00:56:03.820 --> 00:56:07.115
Someone who can keep up with Chewie
and me appreciates the Falcon.

819
00:56:07.240 --> 00:56:09.017
Are you offering me a job?

820
00:56:09.117 --> 00:56:11.619
I wouldn't be nice to you.
Doesn't pay much.

821
00:56:11.745 --> 00:56:13.580
You're offering me a job.

822
00:56:14.789 --> 00:56:16.291
I'm thinking about it.

823
00:56:19.961 --> 00:56:21.129
Well?

824
00:56:25.633 --> 00:56:28.303
If you were. I'd be flattered.
But I have to get home.

825
00:56:29.220 --> 00:56:30.722
Where. Jakku?

826
00:56:31.306 --> 00:56:33.099
I've already been away too long.

827
00:56:34.809 --> 00:56:37.187
Chewie. check out the ship
as best you can.

828
00:56:37.312 --> 00:56:38.521
(CHEWIE GRUNTS)

829
00:56:40.899 --> 00:56:43.818
That's too bad. Chewie kind of likes you.

830
00:56:46.905 --> 00:56:50.200
- FINN: Solo. why are we here again?
- HAN: To get your droid on a clean ship.

831
00:56:50.325 --> 00:56:51.267
REY: Clean?

832
00:56:51.367 --> 00:56:54.245
HAN: You think it was luck
that Chewie and I found the Falcon?

833
00:56:54.913 --> 00:56:58.875
If we can find it on our scanners
the First Order's not far behind.

834
00:56:59.000 --> 00:57:01.778
Wanna get BB-8 to the Resistance?

835
00:57:01.878 --> 00:57:03.713
Maz Kanata's our best bet.

836
00:57:04.589 --> 00:57:06.074
FINN: We can trust her. right?

837
00:57:06.174 --> 00:57:07.717
HAN: Relax. kid.

838
00:57:07.842 --> 00:57:10.512
She's run this watering hole
for a thousand years.

839
00:57:11.262 --> 00:57:14.749
Maz is a bit of an acquired taste.
so let me do the talking.

840
00:57:14.849 --> 00:57:16.584
And whatever you do. don't stare.

841
00:57:16.684 --> 00:57:17.727
BOTH: At what?

842
00:57:18.770 --> 00:57:19.854
Any of it.

843
00:57:22.273 --> 00:57:24.275
(MELLOW MUSIC PLAYING)

844
00:57:26.903 --> 00:57:29.364
(INDISTINCT CHATTER)

845
00:57:41.042 --> 00:57:43.044
- Han Solo!
- (MUSIC STOPS)

846
00:57:43.211 --> 00:57:45.171
- (GLASS SHATTERS)
- (CHATTER CEASES)

847
00:57:47.215 --> 00:57:48.466
(SOFTLY) Oh. boy.

848
00:57:48.591 --> 00:57:49.759
Hey. Maz.

849
00:57:50.593 --> 00:57:51.886
(MUSIC AND CHATTER RESUME)

850
00:57:53.596 --> 00:57:55.557
Where's my boyfriend?

851
00:57:56.057 --> 00:57:57.667
Chewie's working on the Falcon.

852
00:57:57.767 --> 00:57:58.768
I like that Wookiee.

853
00:57:59.561 --> 00:58:01.504
I assume you need something.

854
00:58:01.604 --> 00:58:03.006
Desperately.

855
00:58:03.106 --> 00:58:04.107
Let's get to it.

856
00:58:08.820 --> 00:58:10.446
(BB-8 CHIRPING)

857
00:58:12.574 --> 00:58:14.517
(SPEAKING ALIEN DIALECT)

858
00:58:14.617 --> 00:58:15.618
(GRUNTS)

859
00:58:19.414 --> 00:58:21.082
(LAUGHING)

860
00:58:21.207 --> 00:58:23.318
(ALL CHITTERING)

861
00:58:23.418 --> 00:58:25.253
(CREATURE EXCLAIMS)

862
00:58:29.424 --> 00:58:31.301
(SPEAKING ALIEN DIALECT)

863
00:58:39.434 --> 00:58:41.185
(SPEAKING ALIEN DIALECT)

864
00:58:58.661 --> 00:59:00.121
KYLO REN: Forgive me.

865
00:59:02.790 --> 00:59:04.459
I feel it again.

866
00:59:08.129 --> 00:59:09.672
The pull to the light.

867
00:59:12.508 --> 00:59:15.011
Supreme Leader senses it.

868
00:59:16.095 --> 00:59:17.472
Show me again.

869
00:59:17.972 --> 00:59:20.141
The power of the darkness.

870
00:59:21.434 --> 00:59:24.020
And I will let nothing stand in our way.

871
00:59:24.979 --> 00:59:26.356
Show me...

872
00:59:28.524 --> 00:59:29.859
Grandfather...

873
00:59:32.320 --> 00:59:34.656
and I will finish...

874
00:59:34.781 --> 00:59:36.157
what you started.

875
00:59:48.962 --> 00:59:50.380
- (BB-8 CHIRPS)
- MAZ: A map.

876
00:59:51.005 --> 00:59:53.116
To Skywalker himself?

877
00:59:53.216 --> 00:59:55.952
(CHUCKLES) You are right back in the mess.

878
00:59:56.052 --> 00:59:59.514
Maz. I need you to get this droid to Leia.

879
01:00:00.348 --> 01:00:01.349
Hmm...

880
01:00:01.474 --> 01:00:02.475
No.

881
01:00:03.851 --> 01:00:07.855
You've been running away
from this fight for too long.

882
01:00:08.356 --> 01:00:09.299
Han.

883
01:00:09.399 --> 01:00:11.526
(SPEAKING ALIEN DIALECT)

884
01:00:12.026 --> 01:00:13.528
Go home.

885
01:00:14.195 --> 01:00:15.471
Leia doesn't wanna see me.

886
01:00:15.571 --> 01:00:17.782
Please. we came here for your help.

887
01:00:19.033 --> 01:00:20.034
What fight?

888
01:00:21.244 --> 01:00:23.271
The only fight.

889
01:00:23.371 --> 01:00:25.523
Against the dark side.

890
01:00:25.623 --> 01:00:29.168
Through the ages
I've seen evil take many forms.

891
01:00:30.253 --> 01:00:32.447
The Sith. The Empire.

892
01:00:32.547 --> 01:00:35.883
Today. it is the First Order.

893
01:00:36.676 --> 01:00:39.595
Their shadow is spreading
across the galaxy.

894
01:00:39.721 --> 01:00:41.097
We must face them.

895
01:00:41.222 --> 01:00:43.266
Fight them.

896
01:00:43.391 --> 01:00:44.934
All of us.

897
01:00:45.560 --> 01:00:47.128
There is no fight against the First Order.

898
01:00:47.228 --> 01:00:48.354
Not one we can win.

899
01:00:49.564 --> 01:00:50.798
Look around.

900
01:00:50.898 --> 01:00:53.276
There's no chance we haven't
been recognized already.

901
01:00:53.401 --> 01:00:55.611
I bet you the First Order
is on their way right...

902
01:00:55.737 --> 01:00:56.779
(GEARS CLICKING)

903
01:00:56.904 --> 01:00:57.905
What's this?

904
01:00:59.741 --> 01:01:00.742
What are you doing?

905
01:01:01.409 --> 01:01:03.745
- (OBJECTS CLATTERING)
- (BB-8 CHIRPS)

906
01:01:05.455 --> 01:01:06.956
Solo. what is she doing?

907
01:01:07.081 --> 01:01:08.833
I don't know. But it ain't good.

908
01:01:09.000 --> 01:01:10.777
If you live long enough...

909
01:01:10.877 --> 01:01:14.380
you see the same eyes in different people.

910
01:01:15.298 --> 01:01:19.761
I'm looking at the eyes
of a man who wants to run.

911
01:01:22.638 --> 01:01:24.599
You don't know a thing about me.

912
01:01:25.933 --> 01:01:28.936
Where I'm from. What I've seen.

913
01:01:29.604 --> 01:01:32.273
You don't know the First Order like I do.

914
01:01:33.232 --> 01:01:35.385
They'll slaughter us.

915
01:01:35.485 --> 01:01:37.612
We all need to run.

916
01:01:38.738 --> 01:01:39.781
Hmm.

917
01:01:43.951 --> 01:01:45.119
(GRUNTS)

918
01:01:46.079 --> 01:01:47.080
You see those two?

919
01:01:47.789 --> 01:01:50.942
They'll trade work for transportation
to the Outer Rim.

920
01:01:51.042 --> 01:01:53.252
There. you can disappear.

921
01:01:53.461 --> 01:01:54.462
REY: Finn?

922
01:01:56.881 --> 01:01:57.882
Come with me.

923
01:01:58.925 --> 01:02:00.952
What about BB-8? We're not done yet.

924
01:02:01.052 --> 01:02:02.720
We have to get him back to your base.

925
01:02:03.262 --> 01:02:05.098
(BB-8 CHIRPS ANXIOUSLY)

926
01:02:07.809 --> 01:02:09.143
I can't.

927
01:02:17.944 --> 01:02:19.153
Keep it. kid.

928
01:02:29.413 --> 01:02:30.832
Who's the girl?

929
01:02:31.582 --> 01:02:35.336
(MERCENARIES CONVERSING
IN ALIEN DIALECT)

930
01:02:35.795 --> 01:02:37.739
I was told you can get me
to the Outer Rim.

931
01:02:37.839 --> 01:02:38.923
What are you doing?

932
01:02:40.675 --> 01:02:41.676
Don't leave without me.

933
01:02:42.260 --> 01:02:43.594
(MERCENARY GRUNTS)

934
01:02:45.513 --> 01:02:47.331
You can't just go. I won't let you.

935
01:02:47.431 --> 01:02:48.499
I'm not who you think I am.

936
01:02:48.599 --> 01:02:49.667
Finn. what are you talking about?

937
01:02:49.767 --> 01:02:50.810
I'm not Resistance.

938
01:02:51.519 --> 01:02:53.020
I'm not a hero.

939
01:02:56.274 --> 01:02:58.025
I'm a stormtrooper.

940
01:02:59.193 --> 01:03:02.113
Like all of them. I was taken
from a family I'll never know.

941
01:03:02.864 --> 01:03:04.866
And raised to do one thing.

942
01:03:05.575 --> 01:03:08.703
But my first battle. I made a choice.

943
01:03:09.871 --> 01:03:11.706
I wasn't gonna kill for them.

944
01:03:12.373 --> 01:03:15.293
So I ran. Right into you.

945
01:03:16.878 --> 01:03:18.963
And you looked at me like no one ever had.

946
01:03:21.883 --> 01:03:24.177
I was ashamed of what I was.

947
01:03:26.721 --> 01:03:28.723
But I'm done with the First Order.

948
01:03:28.848 --> 01:03:30.641
I'm never going back.

949
01:03:32.727 --> 01:03:34.478
Rey. come with me.

950
01:03:35.563 --> 01:03:36.814
Don't go.

951
01:03:41.986 --> 01:03:43.738
Take care of yourself.

952
01:03:45.531 --> 01:03:47.200
Please.

953
01:03:52.747 --> 01:03:55.124
(MERCENARY SPEAKING ALIEN DIALECT)

954
01:03:58.169 --> 01:03:59.170
(MERCENARY GRUNTS)

955
01:04:00.922 --> 01:04:02.990
YOUNG REY: (FAINTLY) No!

956
01:04:03.090 --> 01:04:05.259
No!

957
01:04:18.564 --> 01:04:21.442
(INDISTINCT) No! Come back!

958
01:04:22.443 --> 01:04:24.237
No!

959
01:04:40.294 --> 01:04:42.129
Come back!

960
01:04:52.473 --> 01:04:54.308
(INDISTINCT) No!

961
01:04:55.643 --> 01:04:56.811
(AIRLOCK CLANKING)

962
01:05:01.482 --> 01:05:02.858
(BB-8 CHIRPS UNCERTAINLY)

963
01:05:20.668 --> 01:05:22.420
(HINGE CREAKING)

964
01:05:41.314 --> 01:05:42.398
(YELPS)

965
01:05:45.276 --> 01:05:47.094
YOUNG REY: (ECHOING) No!

966
01:05:47.194 --> 01:05:48.738
YODA: (ECHOING) Its energy...

967
01:05:52.533 --> 01:05:54.577
- YODA: ...surrounds us...
- MAN: (ECHOING) No!

968
01:05:54.702 --> 01:05:57.038
YODA: ...and binds us...

969
01:06:01.584 --> 01:06:02.585
(MAN SCREAMS)

970
01:06:04.879 --> 01:06:05.988
OBI-WAN: The Force will be...

971
01:06:06.088 --> 01:06:08.049
(LIGHTSABER HUMMING)

972
01:06:15.056 --> 01:06:16.557
YOUNG REY: (ECHOING) No!

973
01:06:16.682 --> 01:06:18.559
Come back!

974
01:06:18.684 --> 01:06:20.186
UNKAR: Quiet. girl.

975
01:06:21.062 --> 01:06:22.063
No!

976
01:06:26.650 --> 01:06:27.651
OBI-WAN: Rey?

977
01:06:29.445 --> 01:06:30.613
(LIGHTSABER ACTIVATING)

978
01:06:32.239 --> 01:06:34.950
OBI-WAN: These are your first steps.

979
01:06:39.914 --> 01:06:40.915
What was that?

980
01:06:43.167 --> 01:06:44.877
I shouldn't have gone in there.

981
01:06:47.129 --> 01:06:49.573
That lightsaber was Luke's.

982
01:06:49.673 --> 01:06:51.467
And his father's before him.

983
01:06:51.592 --> 01:06:55.221
And now. it calls to you.

984
01:06:55.346 --> 01:06:56.764
I have to get back to Jakku.

985
01:06:57.431 --> 01:06:59.100
Han told me.

986
01:07:06.857 --> 01:07:08.884
Dear child.

987
01:07:08.984 --> 01:07:11.012
I see your eyes.

988
01:07:11.112 --> 01:07:14.098
You already know the truth.

989
01:07:14.198 --> 01:07:16.659
Whomever you're waiting for on Jakku...

990
01:07:17.952 --> 01:07:19.954
they're never coming back.

991
01:07:26.001 --> 01:07:29.630
But... there's someone who still could.

992
01:07:32.341 --> 01:07:33.909
(SOFTLY) Luke.

993
01:07:34.009 --> 01:07:37.680
The belonging you seek
is not behind you...

994
01:07:37.805 --> 01:07:39.473
it is ahead.

995
01:07:39.598 --> 01:07:43.144
I am no Jedi. but I know the Force.

996
01:07:43.269 --> 01:07:47.356
It moves through and surrounds
every living thing.

997
01:07:49.275 --> 01:07:50.860
Close your eyes.

998
01:07:53.154 --> 01:07:54.155
Feel it.

999
01:07:55.448 --> 01:07:57.533
The light...

1000
01:07:57.658 --> 01:08:00.035
it's always been there.

1001
01:08:00.161 --> 01:08:02.163
It will guide you.

1002
01:08:04.290 --> 01:08:06.333
The saber. Take it.

1003
01:08:10.337 --> 01:08:12.281
I'm never touching that thing again.

1004
01:08:12.381 --> 01:08:13.883
I don't want any part of this.

1005
01:08:14.008 --> 01:08:15.217
(MAZ STAMMERS)

1006
01:08:17.344 --> 01:08:18.345
Hmm.

1007
01:08:19.346 --> 01:08:20.764
(REY PANTING)

1008
01:08:40.367 --> 01:08:43.871
HUX: (ON PA)
Today is the end of the Republic.

1009
01:08:45.873 --> 01:08:51.378
The end of a regime
that acquiesces to disorder.

1010
01:08:52.671 --> 01:08:56.759
At this very moment.
in a system far from here...

1011
01:08:56.884 --> 01:09:01.722
the New Republic lies to the galaxy...

1012
01:09:01.847 --> 01:09:05.434
while secretly supporting the treachery...

1013
01:09:06.227 --> 01:09:09.547
of the loathsome Resistance.

1014
01:09:09.647 --> 01:09:13.134
This fierce machine
which you have built...

1015
01:09:13.234 --> 01:09:15.069
upon which we stand...

1016
01:09:15.194 --> 01:09:17.555
will bring an end to the Senate!

1017
01:09:17.655 --> 01:09:20.474
To their cherished fleet!

1018
01:09:20.574 --> 01:09:25.020
All remaining systems
will bow to the First Order!

1019
01:09:25.120 --> 01:09:27.623
And will remember this...

1020
01:09:27.748 --> 01:09:32.795
as the last day of the Republic!

1021
01:09:34.588 --> 01:09:36.699
Confirm transfer to manual control.

1022
01:09:36.799 --> 01:09:38.342
OFFICER: Configure!

1023
01:09:38.467 --> 01:09:39.927
HUX: Fire!

1024
01:09:42.805 --> 01:09:44.056
(ENERGY BUILDING)

1025
01:09:44.181 --> 01:09:45.641
(LOW BOOMING)

1026
01:10:17.965 --> 01:10:19.800
(INDISTINCT SCREAMING)

1027
01:10:31.937 --> 01:10:33.147
(FAINT BOOMING)

1028
01:10:33.814 --> 01:10:35.858
- (FAINT BOOMING)
- (CITIZENS EXCLAIMING)

1029
01:10:37.151 --> 01:10:39.278
(ALL CLAMORING)

1030
01:10:39.987 --> 01:10:42.656
CITIZEN: No. What is it?

1031
01:10:42.823 --> 01:10:44.491
(ALL SCREAMING)

1032
01:10:47.995 --> 01:10:49.913
(CRUMPLING EXPLOSIONS)

1033
01:10:58.672 --> 01:10:59.840
FINN: It was the Republic.

1034
01:11:01.008 --> 01:11:02.635
The First Order. they've done it.

1035
01:11:05.012 --> 01:11:06.180
Where's Rey?

1036
01:11:07.389 --> 01:11:08.599
(REY PANTING)

1037
01:11:21.195 --> 01:11:23.347
(BB-8 CHIRPS INQUISITIVELY)

1038
01:11:23.447 --> 01:11:25.699
- What are you doing?
- (BB-8 CHIRPS)

1039
01:11:26.700 --> 01:11:28.894
- You have to go back.
- (CHIRPS INQUISITIVELY)

1040
01:11:28.994 --> 01:11:30.120
I'm leaving.

1041
01:11:30.871 --> 01:11:32.356
- BB-8...
- (CHIRPS)

1042
01:11:32.456 --> 01:11:33.524
No. you can't.

1043
01:11:33.624 --> 01:11:35.776
You have to go back. you're too important.

1044
01:11:35.876 --> 01:11:37.044
They'll help you.

1045
01:11:37.252 --> 01:11:38.462
(ION ENGINES ROARING)

1046
01:11:51.725 --> 01:11:53.018
I've had this for ages.

1047
01:11:57.064 --> 01:11:58.399
Kept it locked away.

1048
01:11:58.857 --> 01:11:59.858
Where'd you get that?

1049
01:12:01.151 --> 01:12:04.238
A good question. For another time.

1050
01:12:05.239 --> 01:12:06.307
Take it.

1051
01:12:06.407 --> 01:12:07.908
Find your friend!

1052
01:12:12.329 --> 01:12:14.206
- (LOW RUMBLING)
- (CHEWIE GROWLS)

1053
01:12:15.082 --> 01:12:17.084
Those beasts.

1054
01:12:17.209 --> 01:12:18.210
They're here.

1055
01:12:18.335 --> 01:12:19.753
(REY PANTING)

1056
01:12:24.925 --> 01:12:26.427
(LASERS FIRING)

1057
01:12:42.109 --> 01:12:44.778
STORMTROOPER: FN-417. hold position.

1058
01:12:46.613 --> 01:12:48.282
- (BLASTER CLICKS)
- Oh. safety.

1059
01:12:55.622 --> 01:12:56.623
(BB-8 CHIRPS LOUDLY)

1060
01:13:00.878 --> 01:13:02.045
(REY YELPS)

1061
01:13:13.974 --> 01:13:15.042
STORMTROOPER: Sir.

1062
01:13:15.142 --> 01:13:16.460
The droid was spotted heading west.

1063
01:13:16.560 --> 01:13:17.561
With a girl.

1064
01:13:23.108 --> 01:13:25.552
You have to keep going. Stay out of sight.

1065
01:13:25.652 --> 01:13:28.472
- I'll try to fight them off.
- (BB-8 CHIRPS NERVOUSLY)

1066
01:13:28.572 --> 01:13:29.823
I hope so. too.

1067
01:13:32.493 --> 01:13:34.495
- (CREATURE GROANS)
- (CHEWIE GROWLS)

1068
01:13:42.252 --> 01:13:44.171
- Come on. Chewie!
- (CHEWIE GRUNTS)

1069
01:13:46.590 --> 01:13:48.575
MAZ: Rey and BB-8! They need you!

1070
01:13:48.675 --> 01:13:49.660
Now! Go!

1071
01:13:49.760 --> 01:13:52.079
I need a weapon!

1072
01:13:52.179 --> 01:13:53.639
You have one!

1073
01:13:56.350 --> 01:13:57.851
(LIGHTSABER ACTIVATING)

1074
01:14:03.023 --> 01:14:05.692
- HAN: Hey. can I try that?
- (CHEWIE GROWLS)

1075
01:14:09.988 --> 01:14:11.323
(STORMTROOPER SCREAMING)

1076
01:14:12.199 --> 01:14:13.659
I like this thing.

1077
01:14:16.328 --> 01:14:17.871
(LIGHTSABER HUMMING)

1078
01:14:19.623 --> 01:14:20.916
STORMTROOPER: Traitor!

1079
01:14:26.880 --> 01:14:28.674
(LIGHTSABER HUMMING)

1080
01:14:30.217 --> 01:14:31.718
- (ENERGY CRACKLING)
- (BOTH GRUNTING)

1081
01:15:00.873 --> 01:15:02.541
- (FINN GASPING)
- (CHEWIE GROWLS)

1082
01:15:05.669 --> 01:15:07.488
- You okay. Big Deal?
- Thanks.

1083
01:15:07.588 --> 01:15:08.589
STORMTROOPER: Don't move.

1084
01:15:09.840 --> 01:15:11.592
TK-338. we have targets in custody.

1085
01:15:11.758 --> 01:15:12.843
(CHEWIE GROWLS)

1086
01:15:14.219 --> 01:15:15.804
(INDISTINCT RADIO CHATTER)

1087
01:15:16.555 --> 01:15:17.664
(ION ENGINES ROARING FAINTLY)

1088
01:15:17.764 --> 01:15:20.000
STORMTROOPER 1: We have incoming at 28. 6.

1089
01:15:20.100 --> 01:15:22.102
STORMTROOPER 2: Move! Move! Move!

1090
01:15:23.103 --> 01:15:26.089
Scramble all squads. repeat.
scramble all squads!

1091
01:15:26.189 --> 01:15:27.941
Head to higher cover and wait
for our position!

1092
01:15:28.108 --> 01:15:29.359
(CHEWIE GROWLS)

1093
01:15:30.777 --> 01:15:32.279
It's the Resistance.

1094
01:15:40.120 --> 01:15:42.356
Go straight at them!
Don't let these dogs scare you!

1095
01:15:42.456 --> 01:15:44.082
- JESS: Copy that.
- SNAP: We're with you. Poe.

1096
01:16:12.819 --> 01:16:13.820
HAN: Quick!

1097
01:16:41.807 --> 01:16:44.101
FINN: Whoo! Yeah!

1098
01:16:44.768 --> 01:16:46.603
That's one hell of a pilot!

1099
01:16:46.770 --> 01:16:48.021
Whoo-hoo!

1100
01:16:50.065 --> 01:16:50.941
(REY PANTING)

1101
01:16:55.445 --> 01:16:56.947
(LEAVES RUSTLING)

1102
01:16:57.823 --> 01:16:58.824
(FAINT WHIRRING)

1103
01:17:00.117 --> 01:17:01.368
(INDISTINCT CHITTER)

1104
01:17:02.703 --> 01:17:03.704
- (LIGHTSABER HUMS)
- (REY GASPS)

1105
01:17:14.172 --> 01:17:15.757
- (LIGHTSABER CRACKLING)
- (REY YELPS)

1106
01:17:15.882 --> 01:17:17.092
(BOLTS DEFLECTING)

1107
01:17:30.647 --> 01:17:31.690
(BOLTS DEFLECTING)

1108
01:17:32.190 --> 01:17:33.233
(REY GASPS)

1109
01:17:36.737 --> 01:17:38.280
(REY STRAINING)

1110
01:17:42.367 --> 01:17:44.411
The girl I've heard so much about.

1111
01:17:49.082 --> 01:17:50.584
(REY GASPING)

1112
01:17:56.673 --> 01:17:58.258
The droid.

1113
01:17:59.926 --> 01:18:02.220
- (LIGHTSABER HUMS)
- Where is it?

1114
01:18:07.434 --> 01:18:09.061
STORMTROOPER: Request air support.

1115
01:18:11.396 --> 01:18:12.939
(LOW HUMMING)

1116
01:18:16.193 --> 01:18:17.569
The map.

1117
01:18:19.529 --> 01:18:21.682
You've seen it.

1118
01:18:21.782 --> 01:18:24.117
STORMTROOPER: Sir. Resistance fighters.

1119
01:18:25.077 --> 01:18:26.661
We need more troops.

1120
01:18:26.787 --> 01:18:28.622
KYLO REN: Pull the division out.

1121
01:18:28.747 --> 01:18:31.792
Forget the droid. We have what we need.

1122
01:18:38.632 --> 01:18:39.925
STORMTROOPER: Pull back to tree line!

1123
01:18:55.315 --> 01:18:56.842
FINN: No!

1124
01:18:56.942 --> 01:18:58.568
(PANTING)

1125
01:19:00.570 --> 01:19:01.988
No. no!

1126
01:19:03.907 --> 01:19:05.992
No! No!

1127
01:19:07.661 --> 01:19:08.995
Rey!

1128
01:19:28.014 --> 01:19:30.016
FINN: He took her. Did you see that?

1129
01:19:30.851 --> 01:19:32.252
He took her. She's gone.

1130
01:19:32.352 --> 01:19:33.520
Yeah. I know.

1131
01:19:33.645 --> 01:19:34.980
(CHEWIE GROWLS)

1132
01:19:42.863 --> 01:19:44.197
RESISTANCE COMMANDER: Let's go.

1133
01:19:57.878 --> 01:20:00.380
C-3PO: Goodness! Han Solo!

1134
01:20:00.505 --> 01:20:02.674
It is I. C-3PO.

1135
01:20:03.216 --> 01:20:06.344
You probably don't recognize me
because of the red arm.

1136
01:20:06.469 --> 01:20:08.371
Look who it is. did you see who...

1137
01:20:08.471 --> 01:20:09.514
(STAMMERS)

1138
01:20:10.182 --> 01:20:11.183
Uh...

1139
01:20:11.725 --> 01:20:12.726
Hmm.

1140
01:20:12.851 --> 01:20:15.879
Excuse me. Prin... General. Sorry.

1141
01:20:15.979 --> 01:20:18.298
- Come along. BB-8. quickly.
- (BB-8 CHIRPS INQUISITIVELY)

1142
01:20:18.398 --> 01:20:21.067
Yes. I must get my proper arm reinstalled.

1143
01:20:22.986 --> 01:20:24.738
HAN: You changed your hair.

1144
01:20:27.073 --> 01:20:28.491
LEIA: Same jacket.

1145
01:20:29.743 --> 01:20:31.536
HAN: No. new jacket.

1146
01:20:33.288 --> 01:20:34.789
(CHEWIE GROWLS SOFTLY)

1147
01:20:36.499 --> 01:20:38.210
(CHEWIE CHATTERING)

1148
01:20:44.507 --> 01:20:45.508
I saw him.

1149
01:20:47.427 --> 01:20:49.596
Leia. I saw our son.

1150
01:20:51.264 --> 01:20:52.557
He was here.

1151
01:21:13.119 --> 01:21:14.663
(INDISTINCT CHATTER)

1152
01:21:26.591 --> 01:21:28.301
(INDISTINCT CHATTER ON PA)

1153
01:21:33.348 --> 01:21:34.349
CREWMAN: Hey!

1154
01:21:36.142 --> 01:21:37.143
(BB-8 CHIRPS HAPPILY)

1155
01:21:38.937 --> 01:21:40.814
BB-8. my buddy.

1156
01:21:40.939 --> 01:21:42.883
- Oh. it's so good to see you.
- (BB-8 CHIRPING)

1157
01:21:42.983 --> 01:21:43.967
Finn saved you?

1158
01:21:44.067 --> 01:21:45.151
- Where is he?
- (CHIRPS)

1159
01:21:45.277 --> 01:21:46.486
Poe?

1160
01:21:48.029 --> 01:21:49.030
(LAUGHING) Oh. no.

1161
01:21:49.531 --> 01:21:51.057
Poe Dameron. you're alive?

1162
01:21:51.157 --> 01:21:53.310
- Buddy! So are you!
- What happened to you?

1163
01:21:53.410 --> 01:21:54.728
I got thrown from the crash.

1164
01:21:54.828 --> 01:21:56.730
I woke up at night.
No you. No ship. Nothing.

1165
01:21:56.830 --> 01:21:58.206
BB-8 says that you saved him.

1166
01:21:58.331 --> 01:21:59.833
No. no. no. It wasn't just me.

1167
01:21:59.958 --> 01:22:01.443
You completed my mission. Finn...

1168
01:22:01.543 --> 01:22:02.544
That's my jacket.

1169
01:22:02.711 --> 01:22:05.071
- Oh...
- No. no. no.

1170
01:22:05.171 --> 01:22:06.923
Keep it. It suits you.

1171
01:22:07.799 --> 01:22:09.551
You're a good man. Finn.

1172
01:22:10.468 --> 01:22:12.429
Poe. I need your help.

1173
01:22:13.972 --> 01:22:16.808
ANNOUNCER: (ON PA)
PZ-4CO. report to communications.

1174
01:22:19.894 --> 01:22:20.895
POE: General Organa...

1175
01:22:22.731 --> 01:22:24.858
I'm sorry to interrupt. This is Finn.

1176
01:22:24.983 --> 01:22:27.802
- He needs to talk to you.
- And I need to talk to him.

1177
01:22:27.902 --> 01:22:29.679
That was incredibly brave what you did.

1178
01:22:29.779 --> 01:22:32.365
Renouncing the First Order.
saving this man's life.

1179
01:22:32.490 --> 01:22:34.367
Thank you. ma'am. But a friend
of mine was taken prisoner.

1180
01:22:34.492 --> 01:22:36.353
Han told me about the girl.

1181
01:22:36.453 --> 01:22:37.579
I'm sorry.

1182
01:22:37.704 --> 01:22:39.731
Finn's familiar with the weapon
that destroyed the Hosnian system.

1183
01:22:39.831 --> 01:22:40.832
He worked on the base.

1184
01:22:41.333 --> 01:22:43.251
We're desperate for anything
you can tell us.

1185
01:22:43.376 --> 01:22:44.611
That's where my friend was taken.

1186
01:22:44.711 --> 01:22:46.004
I've got to get there fast.

1187
01:22:46.129 --> 01:22:49.883
And I will do everything I can to help but
first you need to tell us all you know.

1188
01:22:50.050 --> 01:22:51.593
(CHEWIE CHATTERING)

1189
01:22:52.886 --> 01:22:54.596
That sounds very scary.

1190
01:22:54.721 --> 01:22:56.056
(GROWLS)

1191
01:22:56.723 --> 01:22:58.850
You must be so brave.

1192
01:22:59.017 --> 01:23:00.352
(GRUNTS IN AGREEMENT)

1193
01:23:01.686 --> 01:23:02.687
C-3PO: General...

1194
01:23:02.812 --> 01:23:05.882
I regret to inform you.
but this map recovered from BB-8...

1195
01:23:05.982 --> 01:23:07.467
is only partially complete.

1196
01:23:07.567 --> 01:23:11.304
And even worse. it matches
no charted system on record.

1197
01:23:11.404 --> 01:23:15.116
We simply do not have enough
information to locate Master Luke.

1198
01:23:16.201 --> 01:23:19.287
Can't believe I was so foolish to think
I could find Luke and bring him home.

1199
01:23:19.412 --> 01:23:20.522
Leia.

1200
01:23:20.622 --> 01:23:21.690
Don't do that.

1201
01:23:21.790 --> 01:23:22.983
Do what?

1202
01:23:23.083 --> 01:23:24.209
Anything.

1203
01:23:25.627 --> 01:23:27.504
C-3PO: Princesses.

1204
01:23:27.629 --> 01:23:29.155
I'm trying to be helpful.

1205
01:23:29.255 --> 01:23:30.240
(CHUCKLES)

1206
01:23:30.340 --> 01:23:31.408
When did that ever help?

1207
01:23:31.508 --> 01:23:33.218
- And don't say the Death Star.
- (HAN SIGHS)

1208
01:23:40.266 --> 01:23:42.227
(BB-8 CHIRPS INQUISITIVELY)

1209
01:23:46.648 --> 01:23:48.341
- (BANGING)
- (CHIRPING)

1210
01:23:48.441 --> 01:23:49.442
C-3PO: BB-8.

1211
01:23:49.567 --> 01:23:52.595
- You're wasting your time.
- (CHIRPING)

1212
01:23:52.695 --> 01:23:55.782
It is very doubtful that R2 would have
the rest of the map in his backup data.

1213
01:23:55.949 --> 01:23:58.059
- (CHIRPING)
- I am afraid not.

1214
01:23:58.159 --> 01:24:02.205
R2-D2 has been in low-power mode
ever since Master Luke went away.

1215
01:24:04.791 --> 01:24:08.044
Sadly. he may never be his old self again.

1216
01:24:08.628 --> 01:24:09.654
(CHIRPS SADLY)

1217
01:24:09.754 --> 01:24:11.381
HAN: Listen to me. will you?

1218
01:24:12.382 --> 01:24:14.717
I know every time you...

1219
01:24:16.928 --> 01:24:19.289
Every time you look at me
you're reminded of him.

1220
01:24:19.389 --> 01:24:21.374
You think I want to forget him?

1221
01:24:21.474 --> 01:24:23.143
I want him back.

1222
01:24:23.268 --> 01:24:25.353
There's nothing more we could have done.

1223
01:24:27.105 --> 01:24:28.465
There's too much Vader in him.

1224
01:24:28.565 --> 01:24:31.468
That's why I wanted him
to train with Luke.

1225
01:24:31.568 --> 01:24:33.261
I just never should have sent him away.

1226
01:24:33.361 --> 01:24:34.946
That's when I lost him.

1227
01:24:36.197 --> 01:24:38.199
That's when I lost you both.

1228
01:24:40.285 --> 01:24:42.954
We both had to deal with it
in our own way.

1229
01:24:43.955 --> 01:24:46.916
I went back to the only thing
I was ever any good at.

1230
01:24:47.500 --> 01:24:48.710
We both did.

1231
01:24:50.920 --> 01:24:52.655
We lost our son.

1232
01:24:52.755 --> 01:24:53.907
Forever.

1233
01:24:54.007 --> 01:24:55.008
No.

1234
01:24:55.133 --> 01:24:56.676
It was Snoke.

1235
01:24:57.135 --> 01:24:59.746
He seduced our son to the dark side.

1236
01:24:59.846 --> 01:25:01.431
But we can still save him.

1237
01:25:02.140 --> 01:25:03.266
Me.

1238
01:25:04.184 --> 01:25:05.226
You.

1239
01:25:06.060 --> 01:25:08.380
If Luke couldn't reach him. how could I?

1240
01:25:08.480 --> 01:25:09.898
Luke is a Jedi.

1241
01:25:11.483 --> 01:25:12.817
You're his father.

1242
01:25:15.528 --> 01:25:19.307
There is still light in him. I know it.

1243
01:25:19.407 --> 01:25:21.101
STATURA: General...

1244
01:25:21.201 --> 01:25:23.703
the reconnaissance report
on the enemy base is coming.

1245
01:25:36.341 --> 01:25:37.550
(ION ENGINES ROARING)

1246
01:25:44.474 --> 01:25:46.309
- (METAL CLANGS)
- (REY GASPS)

1247
01:25:50.522 --> 01:25:51.523
Where am I?

1248
01:25:53.858 --> 01:25:55.176
You're my guest.

1249
01:25:55.276 --> 01:25:56.594
Where are the others?

1250
01:25:56.694 --> 01:25:58.346
Do you mean the murderers...

1251
01:25:58.446 --> 01:26:01.324
traitors. and thieves you call friends?

1252
01:26:02.283 --> 01:26:04.744
You'll be relieved to hear I have no idea.

1253
01:26:06.746 --> 01:26:08.831
You still want to kill me.

1254
01:26:09.624 --> 01:26:13.294
That happens when you're being hunted
by a creature in a mask.

1255
01:26:16.339 --> 01:26:17.632
(HELMET HISSING)

1256
01:26:38.236 --> 01:26:40.071
Tell me about the droid.

1257
01:26:40.905 --> 01:26:44.142
He's a BB unit with a selenium drive
and a thermal hyperscan vindicator.

1258
01:26:44.242 --> 01:26:46.352
It's carrying a section
of a navigational chart.

1259
01:26:46.452 --> 01:26:47.812
And we have the rest.

1260
01:26:47.912 --> 01:26:50.857
Recovered from the archives of the
Empire but we need the last piece.

1261
01:26:50.957 --> 01:26:53.418
And somehow you convinced
the droid to show it to you.

1262
01:26:55.044 --> 01:26:56.045
You.

1263
01:26:57.505 --> 01:26:58.756
A scavenger.

1264
01:27:01.092 --> 01:27:03.219
You know I can take whatever I want.

1265
01:27:06.306 --> 01:27:07.599
(REY STRAINING)

1266
01:27:09.350 --> 01:27:11.269
You're so lonely.

1267
01:27:13.271 --> 01:27:14.772
So afraid to leave.

1268
01:27:18.943 --> 01:27:21.863
At night. desperate to sleep.

1269
01:27:24.991 --> 01:27:26.576
You imagine an ocean.

1270
01:27:27.535 --> 01:27:28.828
I see it.

1271
01:27:30.079 --> 01:27:31.831
I see the island.

1272
01:27:36.419 --> 01:27:37.712
And Han Solo.

1273
01:27:40.048 --> 01:27:42.216
You feel like he's the father
you never had.

1274
01:27:42.842 --> 01:27:44.344
He would have disappointed you.

1275
01:27:44.469 --> 01:27:45.762
Get out of my head.

1276
01:27:46.888 --> 01:27:48.431
I know you've seen the map.

1277
01:27:50.016 --> 01:27:51.184
It's in there.

1278
01:27:52.101 --> 01:27:53.353
And now you'll give it to me.

1279
01:27:55.188 --> 01:27:56.356
(REY GRUNTS)

1280
01:27:57.982 --> 01:27:59.067
(STRAINING)

1281
01:28:01.986 --> 01:28:04.030
Don't be afraid. I feel it. too.

1282
01:28:06.491 --> 01:28:08.993
I'm not giving you anything.

1283
01:28:09.619 --> 01:28:10.703
We'll see.

1284
01:28:12.538 --> 01:28:13.623
(LOW HUMMING)

1285
01:28:15.249 --> 01:28:16.859
(STRAINING)

1286
01:28:16.959 --> 01:28:17.960
(GASPS)

1287
01:28:31.474 --> 01:28:33.017
(REY STRAINING)

1288
01:28:50.702 --> 01:28:51.703
You.

1289
01:28:52.787 --> 01:28:53.788
You're afraid.

1290
01:28:56.833 --> 01:28:59.752
That you will never be
as strong as Darth Vader.

1291
01:29:00.628 --> 01:29:01.796
(REY EXHALES)

1292
01:29:01.921 --> 01:29:03.589
(KYLO REN SHUDDERS)

1293
01:29:08.928 --> 01:29:12.498
SNOKE: The scavenger... resisted you?

1294
01:29:12.598 --> 01:29:14.167
She is strong with the Force.

1295
01:29:14.267 --> 01:29:16.044
Untrained. but stronger than she knows.

1296
01:29:16.144 --> 01:29:17.337
And the droid?

1297
01:29:17.437 --> 01:29:20.757
Ren believed it was no longer
valuable to us.

1298
01:29:20.857 --> 01:29:23.484
That the girl was all we needed.

1299
01:29:23.609 --> 01:29:26.054
As a result. the droid has
most likely been returned...

1300
01:29:26.154 --> 01:29:27.280
to the hands of the enemy.

1301
01:29:27.405 --> 01:29:29.098
They may have the map already.

1302
01:29:29.198 --> 01:29:32.935
Then the Resistance must be destroyed
before they get to Skywalker.

1303
01:29:33.035 --> 01:29:34.896
HUX: We have their location.

1304
01:29:34.996 --> 01:29:37.623
We tracked their reconnaissance ship
to the Ileenium system.

1305
01:29:38.624 --> 01:29:39.901
Good.

1306
01:29:40.001 --> 01:29:42.862
Then we will crush them once and for all.

1307
01:29:42.962 --> 01:29:44.714
Prepare the weapon.

1308
01:29:45.339 --> 01:29:48.117
Supreme Leader. I can get
the map from the girl.

1309
01:29:48.217 --> 01:29:50.011
I just need your guidance.

1310
01:29:51.637 --> 01:29:55.725
If what you say about this girl is true...

1311
01:29:56.350 --> 01:30:01.022
Bring her to me.

1312
01:30:03.983 --> 01:30:06.027
(INDISTINCT RADIO CHATTER)

1313
01:30:14.994 --> 01:30:17.146
You will remove these restraints...

1314
01:30:17.246 --> 01:30:20.333
and leave this cell with the door open.

1315
01:30:24.086 --> 01:30:25.838
STORMTROOPER: What did you say?

1316
01:30:28.758 --> 01:30:33.012
You will remove these restraints
and leave this cell with the door open.

1317
01:30:39.852 --> 01:30:43.564
STORMTROOPER: I'll tighten
those restraints. scavenger scum.

1318
01:30:57.870 --> 01:31:01.916
You will remove these restraints
and leave this cell with the door open.

1319
01:31:05.628 --> 01:31:09.048
STORMTROOPER: I will remove these restraints
and leave the cell with the door open.

1320
01:31:17.974 --> 01:31:21.002
- And you'll drop your weapon.
- And I'll drop my weapon.

1321
01:31:21.102 --> 01:31:22.270
(BLASTER CLATTERS)

1322
01:31:33.739 --> 01:31:34.824
(SOFTLY) No.

1323
01:31:35.825 --> 01:31:36.826
No.

1324
01:31:37.493 --> 01:31:38.644
(LIGHTSABER ACTIVATING)

1325
01:31:38.744 --> 01:31:39.854
(YELLING) Guards!

1326
01:31:39.954 --> 01:31:41.247
(ELECTRICITY CRACKLING)

1327
01:31:42.415 --> 01:31:43.416
Guards!

1328
01:31:48.421 --> 01:31:50.656
HUX: Begin charging the weapon.

1329
01:31:50.756 --> 01:31:52.074
OFFICER: Yes. sir.

1330
01:31:52.174 --> 01:31:53.467
Weapon charging.

1331
01:31:56.429 --> 01:31:58.097
(ENERGY PULSATING)

1332
01:32:12.737 --> 01:32:16.157
The scan data from Snap's reconnaissance
flight confirms Finn's report.

1333
01:32:16.282 --> 01:32:19.619
They've somehow created a hyper-lightspeed
weapon built within the planet itself.

1334
01:32:19.785 --> 01:32:20.728
A laser cannon?

1335
01:32:20.828 --> 01:32:22.663
We're not sure how to describe
a weapon of this scale.

1336
01:32:22.788 --> 01:32:23.773
EMATT: It's another Death Star.

1337
01:32:23.873 --> 01:32:25.608
I wish that were the case. Major.

1338
01:32:25.708 --> 01:32:26.959
This was the Death Star.

1339
01:32:29.712 --> 01:32:32.214
- And this is Starkiller Base.
- (ALL EXCLAIM)

1340
01:32:32.715 --> 01:32:33.866
So. it's big.

1341
01:32:33.966 --> 01:32:37.053
How is it possible to power
a weapon of that size?

1342
01:32:37.178 --> 01:32:39.305
It uses the power of the sun.

1343
01:32:40.514 --> 01:32:43.876
As the weapon is charged
the sun is drained until it disappears.

1344
01:32:43.976 --> 01:32:44.977
AIDE: Ma'am.

1345
01:32:46.979 --> 01:32:49.565
The First Order. they're charging
the weapon again now.

1346
01:32:50.524 --> 01:32:52.401
Our system is the next target.

1347
01:32:52.526 --> 01:32:53.511
C-3PO: Oh. my.

1348
01:32:53.611 --> 01:32:55.096
Without the Republic fleet. we're doomed.

1349
01:32:55.196 --> 01:32:56.973
Okay. How do we blow it up?

1350
01:32:57.073 --> 01:32:59.392
- There's always a way to do that.
- Han's right.

1351
01:32:59.492 --> 01:33:02.603
STATURA: In order for that amount
of power to be contained...

1352
01:33:02.703 --> 01:33:04.664
that base has to have some
kind of thermal oscillator.

1353
01:33:04.789 --> 01:33:06.958
There is one. Precinct 47.

1354
01:33:07.541 --> 01:33:08.776
Here.

1355
01:33:08.876 --> 01:33:10.836
STATURA:
If we can destroy that oscillator...

1356
01:33:10.962 --> 01:33:13.906
it might destabilize the core
and cripple the weapon.

1357
01:33:14.006 --> 01:33:15.783
- Maybe the planet.
- We'll go in there.

1358
01:33:15.883 --> 01:33:17.218
we'll hit that oscillator
with everything we've got.

1359
01:33:17.343 --> 01:33:20.721
They have defensive shields
that our ships cannot penetrate.

1360
01:33:20.846 --> 01:33:22.248
We disable the shields.

1361
01:33:22.348 --> 01:33:24.016
Kid. you worked there.

1362
01:33:24.141 --> 01:33:25.126
What do you got?

1363
01:33:25.226 --> 01:33:26.419
I can do it.

1364
01:33:26.519 --> 01:33:27.770
I like this guy.

1365
01:33:27.895 --> 01:33:29.755
I can disable the shields.
but I have to be there.

1366
01:33:29.855 --> 01:33:31.299
On the planet.

1367
01:33:31.399 --> 01:33:33.025
- We'll get you there.
- Han. how?

1368
01:33:33.776 --> 01:33:35.277
If I told you. you wouldn't like it.

1369
01:33:35.403 --> 01:33:37.263
POE: So we disable the shields...

1370
01:33:37.363 --> 01:33:39.657
we take out the oscillator
and we blow up their big gun.

1371
01:33:39.782 --> 01:33:41.867
- (CHEWIE ROARS)
- All right. Let's go.

1372
01:33:42.034 --> 01:33:43.285
(ALL CLAMORING)

1373
01:34:04.390 --> 01:34:05.875
Chewie. check that donal capitator.

1374
01:34:05.975 --> 01:34:07.460
Come on. Let's go.

1375
01:34:07.560 --> 01:34:09.770
Finn. be careful with those.
They're explosives.

1376
01:34:09.895 --> 01:34:10.938
FINN: Now you tell me?

1377
01:34:11.063 --> 01:34:14.275
LEIA:
You know. no matter how much we fought...

1378
01:34:15.693 --> 01:34:18.012
I've always hated watching you leave.

1379
01:34:18.112 --> 01:34:19.321
That's why I did it.

1380
01:34:20.573 --> 01:34:22.074
So you'd miss me.

1381
01:34:24.827 --> 01:34:26.620
I did miss you.

1382
01:34:28.080 --> 01:34:29.857
It wasn't all bad. was it?

1383
01:34:29.957 --> 01:34:31.025
Huh?

1384
01:34:31.125 --> 01:34:34.253
Some of it was... good.

1385
01:34:34.420 --> 01:34:36.088
- Pretty good.
- (HAN CHUCKLES)

1386
01:34:39.425 --> 01:34:42.303
- Some things never change.
- True.

1387
01:34:42.845 --> 01:34:44.847
You still drive me crazy.

1388
01:34:54.023 --> 01:34:55.941
If you see our son...

1389
01:34:58.444 --> 01:35:00.112
bring him home.

1390
01:35:05.534 --> 01:35:08.187
STORMTROOPER:
Sir. sensors triggered in Hangar 718.

1391
01:35:08.287 --> 01:35:09.939
We're searching the area.

1392
01:35:10.039 --> 01:35:12.166
KYLO REN:
She's just beginning to test her powers.

1393
01:35:12.291 --> 01:35:15.711
The longer it takes to find her
the more dangerous she becomes.

1394
01:35:20.800 --> 01:35:22.410
ANNOUNCER: (ON PA) All sentry droids...

1395
01:35:22.510 --> 01:35:26.038
all sentry droids. resynchronize
to Galactic Standard Time.

1396
01:35:26.138 --> 01:35:28.140
Offset 473.

1397
01:35:30.893 --> 01:35:31.977
How are we getting in?

1398
01:35:32.103 --> 01:35:34.046
Their shields have
a fractional refresh rate.

1399
01:35:34.146 --> 01:35:37.316
Keeps anything traveling slower
than lightspeed from getting through.

1400
01:35:37.900 --> 01:35:39.985
We're making our landing
approach at lightspeed?

1401
01:35:40.111 --> 01:35:41.320
(CHEWIE GROWLS)

1402
01:35:41.445 --> 01:35:42.530
Chewie. get ready.

1403
01:35:43.823 --> 01:35:44.990
And... Now!

1404
01:35:45.116 --> 01:35:46.242
(THRUSTERS FIRING)

1405
01:35:48.911 --> 01:35:50.579
- (CHEWIE GROWLS)
- I am pulling up!

1406
01:35:57.294 --> 01:35:58.904
- (CHEWIE GROWLS)
- I get any higher...

1407
01:35:59.004 --> 01:36:00.256
they'll see us!

1408
01:36:22.194 --> 01:36:24.572
OFFICER:
Sir. she was not found in Hangar 718.

1409
01:36:24.697 --> 01:36:25.765
But all troops are on alert.

1410
01:36:25.865 --> 01:36:27.241
KYLO REN: Put every hangar on lockdown.

1411
01:36:27.366 --> 01:36:29.034
She's going to try to steal
a ship to esc...

1412
01:36:31.662 --> 01:36:33.205
(SOFTLY) Han Solo.

1413
01:36:44.425 --> 01:36:46.118
The flooding tunnel is over that ridge.

1414
01:36:46.218 --> 01:36:47.453
We'll get in that way.

1415
01:36:47.553 --> 01:36:49.455
What was your job
when you were based here?

1416
01:36:49.555 --> 01:36:50.556
Sanitation.

1417
01:36:53.434 --> 01:36:55.127
- Sanitation?
- (CHEWIE GRUNTS)

1418
01:36:55.227 --> 01:36:56.937
Then how do you know
how to disable the shields?

1419
01:36:57.062 --> 01:36:58.063
I don't.

1420
01:36:58.189 --> 01:36:59.940
I'm just here to get Rey.

1421
01:37:00.065 --> 01:37:03.636
People are counting on us.
The galaxy is counting on us.

1422
01:37:03.736 --> 01:37:05.070
Solo. we'll figure it out.

1423
01:37:06.030 --> 01:37:07.448
We'll use the Force.

1424
01:37:07.573 --> 01:37:09.642
That's not how the Force works.

1425
01:37:09.742 --> 01:37:11.118
(CHEWIE GROWLS)

1426
01:37:11.243 --> 01:37:13.787
- Oh. really? You're cold?
- (CHEWIE GRUMBLING)

1427
01:37:13.954 --> 01:37:14.955
FINN: Come on.

1428
01:37:22.379 --> 01:37:23.656
Report.

1429
01:37:23.756 --> 01:37:25.966
Weapon charged in 15 minutes. sir.

1430
01:37:28.427 --> 01:37:29.428
STORMTROOPER: Hey!

1431
01:37:32.598 --> 01:37:34.808
HAN: The longer we're here
the less luck we're gonna have.

1432
01:37:34.934 --> 01:37:37.436
- The shields.
- I have an idea about that.

1433
01:37:43.484 --> 01:37:44.485
(PHASMA GRUNTS)

1434
01:37:45.402 --> 01:37:47.847
- You remember me?
- FN-2187.

1435
01:37:47.947 --> 01:37:49.198
Not anymore.

1436
01:37:49.365 --> 01:37:50.683
The name's Finn and I'm in charge.

1437
01:37:50.783 --> 01:37:52.810
I'm in charge now. Phasma. I'm in charge.

1438
01:37:52.910 --> 01:37:54.895
- Bring it down. Bring it down.
- (WHISPERS) Yeah.

1439
01:37:54.995 --> 01:37:56.121
Follow me.

1440
01:38:09.301 --> 01:38:10.744
STORMTROOPER 1:
Have you checked out the new T-17s?

1441
01:38:10.844 --> 01:38:13.681
STORMTROOPER 2: The T-17s. as far
as I can tell are a great improvement.

1442
01:38:13.806 --> 01:38:15.641
STORMTROOPER 1:
Yeah. That's what they tell you.

1443
01:38:15.766 --> 01:38:16.976
But believe me. they don't hold up.

1444
01:38:17.101 --> 01:38:18.602
- They don't?
- No.

1445
01:38:20.479 --> 01:38:22.189
- (FOOTSTEPS APPROACHING)
- (PANTING)

1446
01:38:24.900 --> 01:38:26.110
(INDISTINCT PA CHATTER)

1447
01:38:33.367 --> 01:38:34.785
(FOOTSTEPS RECEDING)

1448
01:38:46.505 --> 01:38:48.299
(STEAM HISSING)

1449
01:38:54.305 --> 01:38:56.040
FINN: You want me to blast
that bucket off your head?

1450
01:38:56.140 --> 01:38:57.249
Lower the shields.

1451
01:38:57.349 --> 01:38:59.184
PHASMA: You're making a big mistake.

1452
01:38:59.310 --> 01:39:01.395
- Do it.
- (CHEWIE GROWLS)

1453
01:39:02.396 --> 01:39:03.981
(INSTRUMENTS BEEPING)

1454
01:39:05.649 --> 01:39:09.094
Solo. if this works. we're not gonna
have a lot of time to find Rey.

1455
01:39:09.194 --> 01:39:10.571
Don't worry. kid.

1456
01:39:11.363 --> 01:39:12.765
We won't leave here without her.

1457
01:39:12.865 --> 01:39:14.450
(INSTRUMENTS BEEPING)

1458
01:39:14.575 --> 01:39:17.436
You can't be so stupid
as to think this will be easy.

1459
01:39:17.536 --> 01:39:20.105
My troops will storm
this block and kill you all.

1460
01:39:20.205 --> 01:39:22.041
I disagree. What do we do with her?

1461
01:39:22.666 --> 01:39:24.209
Is there a garbage chute?

1462
01:39:24.877 --> 01:39:26.211
Trash compactor?

1463
01:39:27.379 --> 01:39:28.464
Yeah. there is.

1464
01:39:28.797 --> 01:39:30.324
General. their shields are down.

1465
01:39:30.424 --> 01:39:31.992
C-3PO: Thank the Maker!

1466
01:39:32.092 --> 01:39:33.827
LEIA: Han did it. Send them in.

1467
01:39:33.927 --> 01:39:35.829
Give Poe full authorization for attack.

1468
01:39:35.929 --> 01:39:38.207
Black Leader.
go to sub-lights on your call.

1469
01:39:38.307 --> 01:39:39.291
Roger. base.

1470
01:39:39.391 --> 01:39:41.101
Red squad. Blue squad. take my lead.

1471
01:39:41.310 --> 01:39:43.312
- (SPEAKING SULLUSTESE)
- Dropping out of lightspeed.

1472
01:39:57.076 --> 01:39:58.577
POE: (ON RADIO) Almost in range.

1473
01:39:58.744 --> 01:40:01.480
Hit the target dead center.
As many runs as we can get.

1474
01:40:01.580 --> 01:40:03.457
- Approaching target.
- (SPEAKING SULLUSTESE)

1475
01:40:07.419 --> 01:40:08.879
OFFICER 1: Fighters incoming!

1476
01:40:09.755 --> 01:40:11.323
OFFICER 2: (ON PA) Coming at 28.336.

1477
01:40:11.423 --> 01:40:13.200
OFFICER 3:
Forty-five! Shields up! Shields up!

1478
01:40:13.300 --> 01:40:14.968
HUX: Dispatch all squadrons.

1479
01:40:15.094 --> 01:40:16.595
Yes. General.

1480
01:40:17.429 --> 01:40:18.430
All right. Let's light it up.

1481
01:40:28.190 --> 01:40:30.259
- Ah. direct hit. (LAUGHS)
- But no damage!

1482
01:40:30.359 --> 01:40:31.610
POE: (ON RADIO)
Yeah. we gotta keep hitting it.

1483
01:40:31.777 --> 01:40:33.070
Another bombing run.

1484
01:40:33.195 --> 01:40:35.889
Remember. when the sun is gone
that weapon will be ready to fire.

1485
01:40:35.989 --> 01:40:38.575
But as long as there's light.
we got a chance.

1486
01:40:39.118 --> 01:40:40.119
(BB-8 CHIRPING RAPIDLY)

1487
01:40:40.285 --> 01:40:41.829
Guys. we got a lot of company!

1488
01:40:48.460 --> 01:40:50.070
STORMTROOPER:
We think they may be splitting up.

1489
01:40:50.170 --> 01:40:52.131
Heading to quadrants 4 and 5.

1490
01:40:59.972 --> 01:41:01.957
We'll use the charges
to blow that blast door.

1491
01:41:02.057 --> 01:41:04.793
I'll go in and draw fire.
but I'm gonna need cover.

1492
01:41:04.893 --> 01:41:05.961
You sure you're up for this?

1493
01:41:06.061 --> 01:41:07.254
Hell. no.

1494
01:41:07.354 --> 01:41:08.630
I'll go in and try to find Rey.

1495
01:41:08.730 --> 01:41:09.923
The troopers will be on our tail.

1496
01:41:10.023 --> 01:41:12.134
We have to be ready for that.

1497
01:41:12.234 --> 01:41:14.011
There's an access tunnel that leads...

1498
01:41:14.111 --> 01:41:16.638
Why are you doing that? Hmm?
Why are you doing this?

1499
01:41:16.738 --> 01:41:18.073
I'm trying to come up with a plan.

1500
01:41:26.832 --> 01:41:28.083
(LAUGHS)

1501
01:41:33.547 --> 01:41:34.698
(ALL YELP)

1502
01:41:34.798 --> 01:41:36.367
HAN: You all right?

1503
01:41:36.467 --> 01:41:38.077
- Yeah.
- Good.

1504
01:41:38.177 --> 01:41:39.745
FINN:
What happened to you? Did he hurt you?

1505
01:41:39.845 --> 01:41:41.221
Finn. what are you doing here?

1506
01:41:41.346 --> 01:41:43.432
- We came back for you.
- (CHEWIE EXCLAIMS)

1507
01:41:44.308 --> 01:41:45.834
What'd he say?

1508
01:41:45.934 --> 01:41:47.311
That it was your idea.

1509
01:41:51.106 --> 01:41:52.191
Thank you.

1510
01:41:56.069 --> 01:41:57.638
How did you get away?

1511
01:41:57.738 --> 01:41:58.764
I can't explain it.

1512
01:41:58.864 --> 01:42:00.933
And you wouldn't believe it.

1513
01:42:01.033 --> 01:42:03.368
Escape now. hug later.

1514
01:42:10.751 --> 01:42:12.211
(ION ENGINES ROARING)

1515
01:42:18.550 --> 01:42:20.093
I got one behind me.

1516
01:42:20.219 --> 01:42:21.595
- You see it?
- Yeah. I'm on it.

1517
01:42:30.229 --> 01:42:32.064
- Burillo's been hit.
- Watch out for ground fire.

1518
01:42:36.985 --> 01:42:38.929
HAN: They're in trouble.

1519
01:42:39.029 --> 01:42:40.447
We can't leave.

1520
01:42:42.241 --> 01:42:45.227
My friend's got a bag full of explosives.

1521
01:42:45.327 --> 01:42:46.979
Let's use them.

1522
01:42:47.079 --> 01:42:48.455
General. are you seeing this?

1523
01:42:48.580 --> 01:42:49.898
RESISTANCE CONTROLLER:
Two more X-wings down.

1524
01:42:49.998 --> 01:42:52.359
That's half our fleet destroyed.

1525
01:42:52.459 --> 01:42:55.112
C-3PO: And their weapon
will be fully charged in ten minutes.

1526
01:42:55.212 --> 01:42:57.339
It would take a miracle to save us now.

1527
01:43:09.101 --> 01:43:10.102
(CHEWIE GROWLS)

1528
01:43:18.026 --> 01:43:19.027
(REY GRUNTS)

1529
01:43:23.782 --> 01:43:24.766
HAN: Ah.

1530
01:43:24.866 --> 01:43:27.202
- Girl knows her stuff.
- (CHEWIE GROWLS)

1531
01:43:36.169 --> 01:43:38.614
We'll set the charges
against every other column.

1532
01:43:38.714 --> 01:43:39.740
(GROWLS)

1533
01:43:39.840 --> 01:43:41.783
You're right. That's a better idea.

1534
01:43:41.883 --> 01:43:43.869
You take the top. I'll go down below.

1535
01:43:43.969 --> 01:43:45.621
- Detonator.
- (CHEWIE GRUNTS)

1536
01:43:45.721 --> 01:43:47.389
We'll meet back here.

1537
01:44:32.809 --> 01:44:33.810
Find them.

1538
01:45:35.580 --> 01:45:36.581
Ben!

1539
01:45:39.459 --> 01:45:40.502
(BLASTER COCKING)

1540
01:45:43.463 --> 01:45:45.132
(GROWLS)

1541
01:45:49.344 --> 01:45:50.470
Han Solo.

1542
01:45:51.179 --> 01:45:54.057
I've been waiting for this day
for a long time.

1543
01:46:02.941 --> 01:46:03.942
(DOOR OPENING)

1544
01:46:13.326 --> 01:46:16.830
Take off that mask. You don't need it.

1545
01:46:17.414 --> 01:46:19.291
What do you think you'll see if I do?

1546
01:46:19.416 --> 01:46:21.668
The face of my son.

1547
01:46:29.926 --> 01:46:31.511
(HELMET HISSING)

1548
01:46:43.523 --> 01:46:45.692
Your son is gone.

1549
01:46:46.985 --> 01:46:49.321
He was weak and foolish like his father.

1550
01:46:49.488 --> 01:46:51.239
So I destroyed him.

1551
01:46:53.325 --> 01:46:55.702
That's what Snoke wants you to believe.

1552
01:46:56.953 --> 01:46:58.663
But it's not true.

1553
01:46:59.998 --> 01:47:02.067
My son is alive.

1554
01:47:02.167 --> 01:47:03.610
No.

1555
01:47:03.710 --> 01:47:05.904
The Supreme Leader is wise.

1556
01:47:06.004 --> 01:47:08.740
Snoke is using you for your power.

1557
01:47:08.840 --> 01:47:10.634
When he gets what he wants.
he'll crush you.

1558
01:47:15.889 --> 01:47:17.557
You know it's true.

1559
01:47:23.188 --> 01:47:24.172
It's too late.

1560
01:47:24.272 --> 01:47:25.841
No. it's not.

1561
01:47:25.941 --> 01:47:27.692
Leave here with me. Come home.

1562
01:47:29.444 --> 01:47:30.862
We miss you.

1563
01:47:39.579 --> 01:47:41.706
(VOICE BREAKING) I'm being torn apart.

1564
01:47:44.543 --> 01:47:46.711
I want to be free of this pain.

1565
01:47:52.133 --> 01:47:55.387
I know what I have to do. but I don't know
if I have the strength to do it.

1566
01:47:59.307 --> 01:48:00.375
Will you help me?

1567
01:48:00.475 --> 01:48:02.310
Yes. Anything.

1568
01:48:48.690 --> 01:48:49.774
(LIGHTSABER ACTIVATING)

1569
01:48:50.609 --> 01:48:53.428
- (CHEWIE HOWLING)
- REY: No!

1570
01:48:53.528 --> 01:48:55.405
(LIGHTSABER CRACKLING)

1571
01:49:00.368 --> 01:49:01.620
Thank you.

1572
01:49:09.127 --> 01:49:10.128
No.

1573
01:49:45.538 --> 01:49:46.831
(CHEWIE HOWLS)

1574
01:49:47.874 --> 01:49:48.917
(GROANS)

1575
01:49:50.752 --> 01:49:52.087
(CHEWIE ROARS)

1576
01:50:11.815 --> 01:50:13.441
(CRUMPLING EXPLOSIONS)

1577
01:50:25.453 --> 01:50:28.857
The oscillator's been damaged
but is still functional.

1578
01:50:28.957 --> 01:50:31.459
Admiral. their weapon
will fire in two minutes.

1579
01:50:42.721 --> 01:50:44.180
FINN: The Falcon's this way.

1580
01:50:49.060 --> 01:50:50.603
(LIGHTSABER ACTIVATING)

1581
01:50:52.063 --> 01:50:53.398
(LIGHTSABER HUMMING)

1582
01:51:05.076 --> 01:51:06.411
We're not done yet.

1583
01:51:09.581 --> 01:51:11.416
You're a monster.

1584
01:51:11.541 --> 01:51:13.418
It's just us now.

1585
01:51:14.586 --> 01:51:16.087
Han Solo can't save you.

1586
01:51:16.921 --> 01:51:18.256
(KYLO REN GRUNTING)

1587
01:51:24.888 --> 01:51:26.681
- (REY SCREAMING)
- FINN: Rey!

1588
01:51:29.476 --> 01:51:30.961
Rey.

1589
01:51:31.061 --> 01:51:32.062
Rey!

1590
01:51:33.897 --> 01:51:35.507
Oh. no. No. no.

1591
01:51:35.607 --> 01:51:36.591
Rey.

1592
01:51:36.691 --> 01:51:38.193
(LIGHTSABER HUMMING)

1593
01:51:38.818 --> 01:51:40.361
(YELLING) Traitor!

1594
01:51:47.619 --> 01:51:49.370
(LIGHTSABER ACTIVATING)

1595
01:51:50.914 --> 01:51:52.457
That lightsaber.

1596
01:51:53.583 --> 01:51:54.609
It belongs to me.

1597
01:51:54.709 --> 01:51:56.361
Come get it.

1598
01:51:56.461 --> 01:51:57.696
(YELLING)

1599
01:51:57.796 --> 01:51:59.631
(LIGHTSABERS CRACKLING)

1600
01:52:05.136 --> 01:52:06.554
(KYLO REN WINCING)

1601
01:52:17.816 --> 01:52:20.051
(ENERGY CRACKLING)

1602
01:52:20.151 --> 01:52:21.653
(FINN GRUNTS)

1603
01:52:25.490 --> 01:52:26.975
- (FINN GASPING)
- (SIZZLING)

1604
01:52:27.075 --> 01:52:28.993
(FINN SCREAMING)

1605
01:52:30.328 --> 01:52:31.663
(SCREAMING CONTINUES)

1606
01:52:35.834 --> 01:52:37.127
(KYLO REN GRUNTS)

1607
01:52:43.591 --> 01:52:44.592
(FINN GROANS)

1608
01:52:47.011 --> 01:52:48.471
(LIGHTSABER DEACTIVATING)

1609
01:52:49.764 --> 01:52:51.182
(FAINT RUMBLING)

1610
01:52:57.188 --> 01:52:58.189
(GRUNTS)

1611
01:53:18.376 --> 01:53:19.527
(LIGHTSABER ACTIVATING)

1612
01:53:19.627 --> 01:53:21.171
(LIGHTSABER CRACKLING)

1613
01:53:24.632 --> 01:53:25.884
(REY YELLING)

1614
01:53:44.194 --> 01:53:45.278
We just lost R-1.

1615
01:53:45.904 --> 01:53:47.180
JESS: We're overwhelmed.

1616
01:53:47.280 --> 01:53:48.573
What do we do? It isn't working.

1617
01:53:49.324 --> 01:53:51.534
Black Leader. there's a brand
new hole in that oscillator.

1618
01:53:52.577 --> 01:53:54.495
Looks like our friends got in.

1619
01:53:55.121 --> 01:53:56.981
Red Four. Red Six. cover us.

1620
01:53:57.081 --> 01:53:58.233
- I'm on it.
- Roger.

1621
01:53:58.333 --> 01:53:59.859
Everybody else. hit the target hard.

1622
01:53:59.959 --> 01:54:01.002
Give it everything you got.

1623
01:54:13.890 --> 01:54:15.250
I need some help here. I need some help!

1624
01:54:15.350 --> 01:54:16.601
- Coming in!
- Watch out!

1625
01:54:17.810 --> 01:54:19.062
I'm hit!

1626
01:54:24.567 --> 01:54:26.486
All teams. I'm going in.

1627
01:54:26.611 --> 01:54:27.762
Pull up and cover me.

1628
01:54:27.862 --> 01:54:29.614
Copy that. Black Leader. Good luck. Poe.

1629
01:54:35.745 --> 01:54:37.622
Weapon fully charged in 30 seconds.

1630
01:54:39.123 --> 01:54:40.291
Prepare to fire.

1631
01:55:10.697 --> 01:55:12.198
(FAINT RUMBLING)

1632
01:55:22.333 --> 01:55:24.335
- (REY GRUNTING)
- (LIGHTSABERS CRACKLING)

1633
01:55:29.841 --> 01:55:31.009
(KYLO REN GRUNTING)

1634
01:55:40.018 --> 01:55:41.853
(LIGHTSABERS HUMMING)

1635
01:55:52.280 --> 01:55:53.531
(RUMBLING)

1636
01:56:00.705 --> 01:56:01.706
(REY GRUNTING)

1637
01:56:02.874 --> 01:56:03.875
(REY YELPS)

1638
01:56:10.048 --> 01:56:11.799
(LIGHTSABERS CRACKLING)

1639
01:56:11.924 --> 01:56:13.284
(REY STRAINING)

1640
01:56:13.384 --> 01:56:14.802
You need a teacher.

1641
01:56:16.679 --> 01:56:18.473
I could show you the ways of the Force.

1642
01:56:21.100 --> 01:56:22.185
(SOFTLY) The Force?

1643
01:56:23.936 --> 01:56:25.730
(BREATHING SLOWS)

1644
01:56:29.359 --> 01:56:30.902
(BREATHING CALMLY)

1645
01:56:52.006 --> 01:56:53.800
- (LIGHTSABER CRACKLES)
- (KYLO REN GRUNTS)

1646
01:56:55.343 --> 01:56:56.327
(GROANS)

1647
01:56:56.427 --> 01:56:57.804
(YELLS)

1648
01:57:13.111 --> 01:57:15.321
- (LIGHTSABER HUMMING)
- (KYLO REN GROANING)

1649
01:57:19.826 --> 01:57:20.827
(REY YELLS)

1650
01:57:21.285 --> 01:57:23.121
(LIGHTSABER CRACKLING)

1651
01:57:24.455 --> 01:57:25.748
(YELLING)

1652
01:57:33.840 --> 01:57:35.007
(KYLO REN SCREAMS)

1653
01:57:41.097 --> 01:57:42.432
(GROANING)

1654
01:57:44.142 --> 01:57:45.393
(DEEP RUMBLING)

1655
01:58:01.200 --> 01:58:02.201
(LIGHTSABER DEACTIVATES)

1656
01:58:05.621 --> 01:58:07.023
(ALARMS BEEPING)

1657
01:58:07.123 --> 01:58:08.875
(OFFICERS CLAMORING)

1658
01:58:10.960 --> 01:58:14.046
- OFFICER 1: All eyes on that TIE fighter.
- OFFICER 2: We're losing power rapidly!

1659
01:58:16.424 --> 01:58:18.326
DATOO:
Lieutenant! Get back to your station!

1660
01:58:18.426 --> 01:58:21.721
Just look! We won't survive.
Even Hux is gone.

1661
01:58:21.846 --> 01:58:23.347
HUX: Supreme Leader.

1662
01:58:24.223 --> 01:58:26.167
The fuel cells have ruptured.

1663
01:58:26.267 --> 01:58:28.394
The collapse of the planet has begun.

1664
01:58:28.603 --> 01:58:32.648
Leave the base at once
and come to me with Kylo Ren.

1665
01:58:33.733 --> 01:58:35.593
It is time...

1666
01:58:35.693 --> 01:58:38.029
to complete his training.

1667
01:58:40.364 --> 01:58:41.365
Finn!

1668
01:58:42.116 --> 01:58:43.326
Finn.

1669
01:58:53.628 --> 01:58:55.046
(THRUSTERS HUMMING)

1670
01:59:32.458 --> 01:59:35.545
- All teams. I got eyes on them.
- Yes!

1671
01:59:58.484 --> 02:00:01.612
Our job's done here. Let's go home.

1672
02:00:09.787 --> 02:00:11.414
(INDISTINCT CHATTER)

1673
02:00:13.416 --> 02:00:14.625
(CHEWIE GROWLS)

1674
02:00:16.794 --> 02:00:19.130
MEDIC: Easy. easy. He's hurt.

1675
02:00:19.255 --> 02:00:20.464
We've got a heartbeat.

1676
02:00:21.424 --> 02:00:22.466
(CHEWIE GROWLS)

1677
02:01:06.135 --> 02:01:07.345
(CHEWIE MOANS)

1678
02:01:11.349 --> 02:01:12.516
(R2-D2 BEEPING)

1679
02:01:17.188 --> 02:01:20.024
(BB-8 CHIRPS INQUISITIVELY)
(CHIRPING EXCITEDLY)

1680
02:01:20.149 --> 02:01:21.525
(R2-D2 BEEPING)

1681
02:01:22.526 --> 02:01:24.153
- (BB-8 CHIRPING)
- C-3PO: R2-D2!

1682
02:01:25.029 --> 02:01:26.030
You've come back.

1683
02:01:26.989 --> 02:01:28.908
(R2-D2 BEEPING EXCITEDLY)

1684
02:01:29.992 --> 02:01:31.410
- C-3PO: You found what?
- (R2-D2 BEEPS)

1685
02:01:31.535 --> 02:01:33.537
- How dare you call me that!
- (CLANGING)

1686
02:01:34.538 --> 02:01:35.815
(BEEPING RAPIDLY)

1687
02:01:35.915 --> 02:01:37.984
- Find Master Luke. how?
- (BEEPING)

1688
02:01:38.084 --> 02:01:39.110
Come. R2.

1689
02:01:39.210 --> 02:01:41.212
We must go tell the others at once!

1690
02:01:42.546 --> 02:01:43.614
C-3PO: General.

1691
02:01:43.714 --> 02:01:45.883
Excuse me. General.

1692
02:01:46.008 --> 02:01:47.760
(R2-D2 BEEPING)

1693
02:01:50.471 --> 02:01:52.973
R2 may contain some much-needed good news.

1694
02:01:53.641 --> 02:01:55.101
Tell me.

1695
02:02:03.901 --> 02:02:05.386
(BB-8 CHIRPING)

1696
02:02:05.486 --> 02:02:06.904
Yeah. All right. buddy. Hold on.

1697
02:02:21.335 --> 02:02:22.962
C-3PO: The map. it is complete.

1698
02:02:23.587 --> 02:02:25.239
LEIA: Luke.

1699
02:02:25.339 --> 02:02:28.592
C-3PO: Oh. my dear friend.
how I've missed you.

1700
02:02:32.847 --> 02:02:34.014
(RHYTHMIC BEEPING)

1701
02:02:45.568 --> 02:02:47.595
We'll see each other again.

1702
02:02:47.695 --> 02:02:49.613
I believe that.

1703
02:02:57.788 --> 02:02:59.582
Thank you. my friend.

1704
02:03:14.472 --> 02:03:16.307
LEIA: Rey.

1705
02:03:17.975 --> 02:03:20.770
May the Force be with you.

1706
02:03:23.814 --> 02:03:25.065
(BB-8 CHIRPS)

1707
02:03:25.566 --> 02:03:27.568
(CHIRPING INQUISITIVELY)

1708
02:03:44.001 --> 02:03:45.544
(ENGINES FIRING)

1709
02:03:45.669 --> 02:03:47.671
(ALL CHEERING)

1710
02:04:07.858 --> 02:04:09.109
(CHEWIE GROWLS SOFTLY)

1711
02:04:45.187 --> 02:04:46.730
(CHEWIE GROWLS FAINTLY)

1712
02:04:48.315 --> 02:04:49.733
(R2-D2 BEEPS FAINTLY)

1713
02:05:09.169 --> 02:05:10.546
(PANTING)

1714
02:07:07.746 --> 02:07:09.748
(THEME MUSIC PLAYING)

1714
02:07:10.305 --> 02:08:10.576
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today
